\id JOS - Ekajuk Bible 
\h Josua 
\toc1 Nwer nyi Josua 
\toc2 Josua 
\toc3 Jos 
\mt1 Josua 
\c 1  
\s1 Jehova Ka Josua Elkahn Re Á Rod Anebe Isreel Song Go Kenan. 
\p  
\v 1 Ngare nyi Mosis nlokeltum no Jehova ma kpo, owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Josua mmona Nun, ekpeele ji Mosis re:  
\v 2 <<Mosis nlokeltum ewame ebkpo. Wo, a ane baa kpee, tooben ebjing, wahn song siiri aya ma Jodan, rehng go edi ndi ji m bahke kake anebe Isreel.  
\v 3 Edi ajehng ajehng ji a kadde akpade enya, m bahke faake kak-a go abo, ana n nyame tong Mosis.  
\v 4 Edi ndi ejahne bahke bomo go elka emahng ejang eboblum rehng go awong Lebanon go ejang ebobkal, fvfo bomo go agburu aya ma Yufritis go ero nfam, song rehng go ndi nyi anebe Hid, rehng aya ma ki kpi egbuk go erede nfam.  
\v 5 Nnene limm no bahke ma yiimi abohng a na, afung nya a kpeka li go elkpin. Ana n jolo a Mosis, ano wo fvfo m bahke tob jol a na. Me wa nehm tiki yake abo, jol wa nehm tiki ten.  
\v 6 <<Bel atahne, a ekakeltim, tibre wo wo li nne no bahke tohko ane baa tete bo song yel go edi ndi elehkelkv, ji n nyame tong babnde ebo ba nkul re, m bahke kake bo.  
\v 7 Bel na bel atahne, wo sahb bˈbel esahbeltim, jo kunu ekpu wo bum atahm nya Mosis nlokeltum ewame ka-a no. Ka gbake je ejang eboblum, afi ejang ebobkal, eji lˈnob a na edi ajehng ajehng ji a fi no.  
\v 8 Ka tiki rahke nwer atahm nyia go ellungu ngare anyehng anyehng. Jo tir bade, atv a njul, eji a lˈjo kunu ekpu fere jo lim ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo nyono o. Owo a bahke gboko afang, fere nˈnob a na.  
\v 9 Wa n ka ka elkahna? Bel atahne, wo bel esahbeltim. Ka fahl, abo ki-a woono, tibre Jehova Esowo eba, bahke jolo a na edi ajehng ajehng ji a fi no.>>  
\v 10 Owo Josua kehm kake atubesi abanoko ebta ba kpo fili ane elkahn re:  
\v 11 <<Song yelen go atahng edi erekekv, wahn tong ane re, <Tooben nsol alehke enyahne bum, lˈbiingi nfung era, ḿ bahke siiri Jodan, song ko edi ndi ji Jehova Esowo ebahne ka-n no re jol jˈjahne.> >>  
\v 12 Josua kehm lungu ane ba lohng go etˈtohngo ji Ruben, a ji Gad, a ejang etˈtonhgo ji Manase, kehm tongo bo re,  
\v 13 <<Buumen ejehke ji Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova ka-n no: <Jehova Esowo ebahne bahk-n kake erekekv. Á ma-n ka edi ndi jia.>  
\v 14 Akal ebahne, a abon ebahne, a atohkondi atohkondi enyahne kpee bahke ma jol go edi ji Mosis ka-n no, go ero bio bi aya ma Jodan. Abanokebta ebahne kpee, a nsol ebta ebo kpee go ebo abo, bahke gboko atˈtohngo nyako mbang siiri Jodan. Wahn bahke kake abonane ebahne ebo,  
\v 15 tete Jehova ka bo erekekv ana á ma-n ka, eji bo lˈko nji go edi ndi ebo, ji Jehova Esowo ebahne bahke kake bo. Ń lˈlim ano, wahn kehm feere go egahna ndi nyi Mosis nloketuma Jehova ka-n no, go egbuk jehko ji aya ma Jodan, ejang bio bi njul kpo lohng.  
\v 16 Ane bao kehm faange Josua re, <<Ejum ajehng ajehng ji a lꞌka elkahn re wahr lim, e bahke limi, fvfo edi ajehng ajehng ji a lꞌtum-r, e bahke jeke.  
\v 17 Ana e jo wuku Mosis go ejum ajehng ajehng, ano wo fvfo e bahke tob jo wuk-a. Nong lub jol re Jehova Esowo eba bahke jolo a na ana á jolo a Mosis.  
\v 18 Nne no lˈsiir-a go asi, kˈbum alum enya, go ejum ajehng ajehng ji a lꞌtong bo, bo bahk-e wulu. Li re wo bel atahne, a esahbeltim. >> 
\c 2  
\s1 Rehab behre ane ba weele ba nyehn ejahbe 
\p  
\v 1 Josua mmon no Nun kehm tumu ane abal mbehrbehr eji bo jolo go Sitehm re bo song weele nyehn edi ndi jio, asehngesehnge Jeriko. Owo bo kehm tahme, song yel etahk nnenkal asˈsa no bo jo lung-e re Rehab, song jol o.  
\v 2 Bo kehm tongo ntula Jeriko re, <<Nyehno! anebe Isreel bandiki ebba a atv maa, re bo ba weele nyehn ejahbe.>>  
\v 3 Ntula Jeriko kehm tiingi tv Rehab re, <<Yehke ane bao ba ma ba yel go ega etahk, tibre bo ba re bo ba weele nyehn ejahbe kpee.>>  
\v 4 Wo Rehab ebrod ane abal bao behr, kehm bungu re, <<Ee, aneblum baa lˈlohng ba a egame, me n kahnem edi ji bo lohngo no ba.  
\v 5 Bo feere ebo ngare elgung, ngare nyi bo kpo bam eti mbu. N kahnem esi mbang ji bo sehnge sehng tahm. Toonen bo elwaare elwaare. Ḿ bahke ma kpiri bo go mbang.>>  
\v 6 Wo, ga yebrod aneblum bao song kunu go ero elbulu, fere behr bo go nkahr nyi bo yale go ero elbulu.  
\v 7 Ane ba ntul tumu no kehm mehle asongo re bo song seb abaweele nyehn ejahbe mbang mbang nyi li feere elga ni bo kpo siiri aya ma Jodan. Ana ane ba jo seb bo mehle asongo, ano wo bo bame eti mbu.  
\v 8 Re abaweele nyehn adi kehm noongo lal, Rehab song kpiri bo go ero elbulu,  
\v 9 kehm tongo bo re, <<N kpˈkahne re, Jehova ma-n ka edi ndi jia, e kpi egburu elfahle bade anahne. Wo ane kpee ba li ejahbe jia, ebgbo awo, tib eji e kp-n fahle.  
\v 10 Tibre wahr ebwuk ana ji Jehova limi no, Aya nkpafa ka wum kpee, ka-n mbang eji ń lohngo go Ijib abake, fere wuk bade ana ń limi Sihon, a Og atul abal ba anebe Amor ba jolo go ero nfam bi aya ma Jodan, bo ji ń wulu ane ebo kpee.  
\v 11 Eji e wuku nsol nyia kpee, ntim enyahre ebrannge, eko ma-r tan, tib eji e kp-n fahle. Tib Jehova, Esowo ebahne, ye ntahng ntahng wo li Esowo go elbung a ndi.  
\v 12 Wahn fvfo tiren tong-m anv, go mbing nyi Jehova re ḿ bahke tibi ane ebame nnoobo, eji m ma lim nnoobo ka-n. Tib-m wahn ellingi ni m bahk kahne re,  
\v 13 ń nehm wul nsoo, nnee, a abonanee ba nlum a ba nkal , a ane kpee ba bo kpi no, re a bahk-r tahre yehke go elkv.>>  
\v 14 Owo aneblum bao kehm-e tongo re, <<Wahr ebtoobo ebjing re wahr ka elkpin enahre go egahne elkpin, jol tete e kpo. A tohko tong nne awohng awohng ji e ba a, ngare nyi Jehova lꞌka-r ndi nyia e bahk-a fili nobnob, fere fil-a go etingitingi.>>. 
\p  
\v 15 Eji etahk Rehab kuumu go ekahme ji bo si sennge ejahbe kak, Rehab kehm koko ekehd, kahn ewindu ane bao taare badde njahm ekahme nyehko.  
\v 16 Rehab kehm tongo ane bao re, <<Songen go awong, wahn song biiri o nfung era, eji ane ba kp-n sebe lꞌki-n nyehn. Bo lꞌfeere wahn kehm lohngo song.>> 
\p  
\v 17 Aneblum bao kehm bungu tong-e re, <<Nwongo nyi a lim-r no e tir, wahr nehm tuunu,  
\v 18 sehngem re eji e ma yel go ejahbe, e bahke nyehne mbilibili ekehd jia , ji a ma kahn go ewindu ji a yehk-r no yake, a bahke tob ko nso, nne, a abonane ba nlum, a anebe etahk nso kpee, ba bum go ega etahk.  
\v 19 Nne awohng awohng no lˈlohng go ega etahk jo yannge go mbang, alung eme bahke kuumu go ege esi. Ebi jˈjahre nehm jol. Nne awohng awohng no lˈwoomo etahk a na, alung eme bahke kuumu go egahre esi, ebo abehng abehng lˈkoor-e.  
\v 20 Wo a lˈfere tooro ejum ji e kpꞌlimi a tong nne awohng awohng, e bahke foro go nwongo nyi e limi a na.>> 
\p  
\v 21 Rehab kehm faange re, <<Me n taame ji ḿ ma bung.>> A kehm yake bo, bo tahm kehnge. Rehab kehm kahne mbilibili ekehd go ewindu. 
\p  
\v 22 Eji bo tahme no, bo song biiri go awong, kang nfung era o, tete ane bao ba jo seb bo mbang mbang, feere kehnge, bo nyehnem bo.  
\v 23 Ano wo ane abal baa soro badde go ero awong, jo feere ebo kehnge. Bo ba siiri aya ma Jodan, kehm ba tong Josua mmon no Nun nsol kpee nyi ma lim bo.  
\v 24 Bo kehm bungu tong Josua re, <<Jehova ebfaake ejahbe jia kpee go etingitingi kak-r go egahre abo. Ane kpee eko ebtan bo, tib go elfahle ni bo kp-r fahle.>> 
\c 3  
\s1 Anebe Isreel siiri Jodan 
\p  
\v 1 Efungfu behre behre Josua a Isreel kpee kehm mehle go Sitehm song rehng go Jodan, edi ji bo gohro song re ekv kehm siiri aya ma Jodan.  
\v 2 Eji nfung era ma sehng, atubesi abanoko nta kehm mehle jo jen yannge edi erekekv,  
\v 3 kehm kehme ane elkahn ka re, <<Ń lˈnyehn Elkohl Atahm ni egbanngalung ji Jehova Esowo bahne, a abalimajom ba li anebe Levi ma sol, mehlen go adi nya ń jehk no wahn toono elkohl atahm nio.  
\v 4 Ngare nyio nyi, ḿ bahk kahne mbang nyi ḿ bahke sehnge, tibre ń ka sehnga sehng go mbang nyia. Kana jen kabbe elkohl atahm nio, ka-n eyake fee ejum ntahme atahltahl nkpel elon.>> 
\p  
\v 5 Josua kehm tongo ane re, <<Bumen elnahne saang, tibre behna Jehova bahke limi nkpokosi go egahne ellong.>>  
\v 6 Josua kehm bungu tong abalimajom re, <<Roden elkohl atahm ni egbanngalung, wahn gbo ane mbang. Ano wo bo rodo elkohl, gbo bo mbang. 
\p  
\v 7 Jehova kehm bungu tong Josua re, <<Lela wo m bahk-a bomo elmehle wahre go esamahr anebe Isreel kpee, ano wo bo bahke kahne re n li a na, ana n jolo a Mosis.  
\v 8 Tong abalimajom ba solo elkohl atahm re: Bo lˈrehng go nkpe aya mao ma Jodan, bo song yiimen go elka alahb.>> 
\p  
\v 9 Josua kehm bungu tong Isreel kpee re, <<Baan a, wahn ba wuungu atung go alum nya Jehova ma bung, ye ji li Esowo ebahne.  
\v 10 Ana wo ḿ bahke kahne re, Esowo bi li go elkpin wob go egahne ellong. Á bahke kame anebe Kenan, Hid, Hiv, Peres, Girgas, Amor, a anebe Jebus.  
\v 11 Nyehnen, elkohl atahm ni egbanngalung ji Ntul no njini kpee, ni ni bahk-n gboko mbang eji ń kpˈsiiri Jodan.  
\v 12 Anv, yehken ewubu ane abal, nne awohng awohng, go etˈtohngo ajehng ajehng.  
\v 13 Ana abalimajom ba solo elkohl atahm ni Jehova, ye ji li Ntul no njini kpee, bahke behde akpade ebo go aya ma Jodan, alahb bahke kimi ekpidi ebbal, ma kpˈfabe abake bahke ba yiimi gbo ekahme.>> 
\p  
\v 14 Ngare nyi ane ma mehl go edi ekv areke ebo re bo siiri aya ma Jodan, abalimajom ba solo elkohl atahm ni egbanngalung gbo ane mbang.  
\v 15 Jolo ngara nnyel nyi bo kpo kpa nsol ndi, ana akpade nya abalimajom ba solo elkohl atahm rehnge nkpe aya, ana bo behde akpade go nkpe alahb,  
\v 16 alahb ma jo fab ero abake rahke elfabe sa yiimi, lim ekahme bomo go fee go ejahbe ji bo kpo lung re Adam, ji li kohlo Jaretan. Ma jo fab erede erede, fab song yel aya Akang. Ma sa yiimi kpeem jo fab. Ano wo ane male bel mbang siiri sehng aya asongo go Jeriko ji jolo go bo a mbuksong.  
\v 17 Abalimajom ba solo elkohl atahm ni egbanngalung ji Jehova, sa yiimi ndi nyi ma wum, elka aya ma Jodam, tete anebe ejahbe Isreel kpee siiri ewumwum ndi rehng egbuk aya jehko. 
\c 4  
\s1 Anebe Isreel kehm loko eltal ni elbuumu 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ejahbe Isreel kpee ma siiri aya mao ma Jodan mal, owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Josua re,  
\v 2 <<Yehke ewubu aneblum abal, go ellong ane baa, nne awohng awohng go etˈtohngo.  
\v 3 Tong ane bao, bo song rod ewubu atal abal, go yefono edi jio ji abalimajom yiimi no, go elka efabe aya ma Jodan, song bum go edi ji e bahke reke ekv atv ma lela.>>  
\v 4 Josua kehm lungu ewubu ane abal, ba á ma yehke, nne awohng awohng go etˈtohngo,  
\v 5 kehm bungu tong bo re, <<Songen go efabe ji Jodan, esꞌsong bi elkohl atahm ni Esowo yim no, wahn song rod, no nne eltal anehng kunu ekpakebahk, etˈtohngo ajehng ajehng rod eltal anehng anehng,  
\v 6 bahke jolo ejum elliingi go egahne ellong. Go ngare esˈsong, abon ebahne lˈbahb-n re, <Atal nyaa lohngo jen?>  
\v 7 Ḿ bahke tongo bo re, aya ma Jodan kimi ekpidi ebbal. Atal nyaa bahke jolo ejum elbuumu ka anebe Isreel, ngare kpe kpe.  
\v 8 Owo anebe Isreel kehm limi ana Josua ka bo elkahn. Bo yehke ewubu atal abal go elka efabe ji Jodan, jang jang ana nfange atˈtohngo nya Isreel li no, ana Jehova ka Josua elkahn. Bo solo song bum go edi ji bo jo re ekv atv mao, owo bo bumu atal nyao.  
\v 9 Josua fvfo tob lo ewubu atal abal go elka efabe aya ma Jodan, go edi jio ji abalimajom ba solo elkohl atahm ni Esowo yiimi no. Li o tete rehng efung bi lela.  
\v 10 Abalimajom ba solo elkohl atahm ni Esowo yiimi go elka efabe aya Jodan tete ane lim nsol kpee nyi Jehova ka Josua elkahn, ana Mosis tibi Josua. Ane jene elwaare siiri aya,  
\v 11 eji nne awohng awohng ma siiri rehng go egbuk jehko, owo abalimajom tob siiri, a elkohl atahm ni Jehova, ga ane kpee yiimi jꞌrii jo seenge.  
\v 12 Aneblum ba etꞌtohngo ji Ruben a ba Gad, a ejang etꞌtohngo ji Manase tob siiri aya a nsol ebta ebo go ebo abo. Bo gbo anebe Isreel mbang, ana Mosis ka bo elkahn.  
\v 13 Atahntahn ane baa jolo ane atahltahl nkpel atahl alon (40,000), bo siiri aya song rehng go emahng ji Jeriko ji li ebal ebal re bo song nok ebta, fvfo Jehova jolo a bo.  
\v 14 Efung bio Jehova mehle Josua wahre go esamahr bi Isreel kpee. Israel ka Josua ekpunu tete á kpo, ana bo ka Mosis.  
\v 15 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Josua re,  
\v 16 <<Ka abalimajom ba solo elkohl Ntianse elkahn re bo lohng go efabe aya Jodan, ba ga egbuk.  
\v 17 Josua kehm kake abalimajom elkahn re, <<Lohngen go efabe aya Jodan, wahn ba yiimi ga egbuk.>>  
\v 18 Abalimajom kehm lohngo a elkohl atahm ni Jehova ni bo solo no. Ana bo kpˈlohngo go efabe alahb akpade bo ba rehng egbuk, ano wo alahb ma Jodan kpe kehme elfabe, yel rehng egbuk ana wuku wuku.  
\v 19 Nfung ewubu nyi ngbokambanga nnyahng, owo anebe Isreel siiri aya ma Jodan, bo bumu edi erekekv go Gilgal ji li nkonandi nyi Jeriko, ero nfam.  
\v 20 O Gilgal wo Josua lange ewubu atal abal nya bo yehke go elka efabe aya ji Jodan.  
\v 21 Josua kehm bungu tong anebe Isreel re, <<Ngare esˈsong, abon ebahne bahke bahbe babnde re, <Atal nyaa lohngo rejen?>  
\v 22 Tong bo re, <Anebe Isreel siiri efabe Jodan go ewumwum ndi.>  
\v 23 Tibre Jehova, Esowo ebahne, ye wo limi aya ma Jodan ka go egahne esamahr, tete wahn siiri sehng. Jehova Esowo ebahne limi aya ma Jodan, jang jang ana á limi go aya nkpafa, eji á limi no ka egahre esamahr tete e siiri sehng.  
\v 24 Á limi jia eji ane ba njini kpee lˈkahn re ebo bi Jehova kpi nsahm, á tob limi eji wahn fvfo lˈtob jo fahl Jehova ji li Esowo ebahne go njinanjini.>> 
\c 5  
\s1 Anebe Isreel yehke Elbo nrur go Gilgal 
\p  
\v 1 Eji atul bao kpee ba anebe Amor, bo ji li feere erede nfam aya ma Jodan, a atul ba anebe Kenan kpee, bo ji jolo nkpe aya Mediterinian, wuku ana Jehova ma lim aya ma Jodan ma ka, ka anebe Isreel mbang bo siiri efabe aya Jodan, bo kehm kehme elfahle. Bo kpeem bel esahb ji bo bahke yiimi nok a anebe Isreel.  
\v 2 Ngare nyˈnehm o, Jehova kehm tongo Josua re, <<Ko atahntahn atal wo lim abon ntahme, bange yehke anebe Isreel nrur, bo ji bo ki yehke bo nrur wuku wuku.>>  
\v 3 Owo Josua kehm koko atahntahn atal lim abontahme, yehke anebe Isreel nrur go Gibiad Haaralod, ji lohngo re Ewong Nrur ayehke .  
\v 4 Jia ji wahnge Josua limi ano: Tibre ane kpee ba lohngo go Ijib, aneblum kpee ba rehnge ekul bi bo bahke ma je ebta, kpoo kpee go elka emahng ana bo lohngo go Ijib mbang mbang abake.  
\v 5 Aneblum kpee ba lohngo go Ijib, bo yꞌyehke bo nrur. Wo aneblum ba bo jele bo go elka emahng ana bo lohngo go Ijib jo jen asongo go Kena, bo yehkem bo nrur.  
\v 6 Anebe Isreel jene elka emahng nnya atahl abal, tete aneblum kpee ba rehnge ekul bi bo bahke ma je ebta ngare nyi bo lohngo go Ijib, ma kpoo, tib eji bo ki jo kpunu Jehova. Tibre Jehova ko nwongo fere tir re, bo nehm tiki nyehn edi ndi ji á nyame tong babnde re á bahke kake bo. Ndi nyi alahbbel a akehng ekon kpꞌfabe.  
\v 7 Jehova kehm koko abon ebo ba nlum le bo woongo asi nya babnde, bo ba Josua yehke bo nrur, ngare nyio bo ka yehke nrur, tibre bo yehkem bo nrur go mbang.  
\v 8 Eji bo ma yehke aneblum nrur kpee go ejahbe, bo sa o edi erekekv tete alok nrur ebo kpo kpee.  
\v 9 Owo Jehova kehm tongo Josua re, “Lela, me n yehke esono ji ń jolo aju go Ijib go egahne ellong. Bo soro lung edi jio re Gilgal ji lohngo re elyehke wohng go tete rehng lela.  
\v 10 Go ewubu a nfung eni mi nnyahng, ngare elgung, anebe Isreel kehm limi elkak ni Elsehnge Sa, ngare nyi bo kpeka li go edi erekekv ji Gilgal ji li adi ebal ebal nya Jeriko.  
\v 11 Etoono efung, eji elkak Elsehnge Sa ma mal, efung bˈnehm o, anebe Isreel li nsol nyindiki nyi lohng o ndi nyi Kenan: Abred nya bo ki kak ayist, a awokowoko nkohl.  
\v 12 Ana bo li nsol ndi nyia, etoono efung, ano wo mmana rahke no. Mmana kpeem jol ka anebe Isreel, elya nio kpee bo jo li nsol nyi lohng go ndi nyi Kenan. 
\s1 Josua Nyehne Ntubesi Abanoko Ebta No Jehova 
\p  
\v 13 Ngare nyi Josua ma rehng kohlo Jeriko, á kehm tabe amahr enye kehm nyehne nnenlum no yim go egea mbuksong, a ekahngkahng bi á ma wob go mbak. Josua kehm song kpir-e, kehm-e bahbe re, <<A li go egahre ejanga, afi go ejang anebekv ebahre?  
\v 14 Á kehm-e faange re, <<Eˈee n limm ka bo, jol n limm ka wahn. Me wo li ntubesi no abanoko ebta no Jehova, ano wo wahnge m ma ba. Josua kehm gboko kohk esamahr ndi kak-e, kehm-e bahbe re, <<Ntubesi etib abii a kpi no ka nlokeltum ewe?>>  
\v 15 Owo ntubesi no abanoko ebta no Jehova kehm faange re, <<Yehke akpaketa go ega akpade, tib edi ji a yim a, li saang.>> Owo Josua kehm limi no. 
\c 6  
\s1 Anebe Isreel Noko Ga Jeriko 
\p  
\v 1 Ngare nyia Jeriko ebsahd ati mbu ebo kpee, tib esi ji anebe Isreel. Nnene kpeem jo lohng, jol nnene kpeem jo yel.  
\v 2 Owo Jehova kehm tongo Josua re, <<Nyehne! Me n yake Jeriko kpee kak-a go abo, a ntula bo, a abanoko ebta.  
\v 3 Jen sennge Jeriko nkpel anyehng a abanoko ebta kpee. Limen ana, go nfung erakera.  
\v 4 Nong abalimajom na asehma ba fili atang nkom, gbo elkohl atahm mbang. Go efung bi ma biingi nfung esehma, ḿ bahke jene sennge ejahbe jio nkpel na esehma, abalimajom bahke jo wor atang.  
\v 5 Ń lˈwuk abalimajom ma wor atang ekidi ma lab, nong ane biiki wahre wahre; Ekahme ji Jeriko bahke gboko, abanoko ebta bahke sehnge yel go atahng ejahbe, nne awohng awohng bahke jene tor tor yel.  
\v 6 Owo Josua mmona Nun kehm lungu abalimajom, kehm tongo bo re, <<Roden elkohl atahm ni Jehova, nong abalimajom na asehma gbo elkohl atahm nio mbang, fili atang go ebo abo.>>  
\v 7 Josua kehm tongo ane re, <<Mehlen! Jenen sennge ejahbe kak, nong abanoko ebta ba fili nsol ebta gbo elkohl atahm ni Jehova mbang.>>  
\v 8 Eji Josua ma bung abo ano mal, owo abalimajom na asehma, no nne a ntang go esamahr bi Jehova, kehm kehme atang ebo wor ana bo kpˈjene asongo. Elkohl atahm Jehova jo toono bo go njahm.  
\v 9 Abanoko ebta kehm gboko abalimajom ba jo wor atang mbang, egom jehko jo toono elkohl atahm. Ngare nyia kpee bo jo woro atang.  
\v 10 Wo Josua kehm kake ane elkahn re, <<Nnene kˈbiiki ebta, nnene kˈmehl alum wahre, jol nnene ellum ki-e lohng go nnyo tete efung bi á bahke tongo bo re bo biiki, bo kehm biiki.  
\v 11 Á kehm tongo bo rod elkohl atahm ni Jehova jen sennge ejahbe nkpel anyehng efung bio. Ane bao kehm feere kehnge go ebo edi erekekv, song kang atv mao o.  
\v 12 Josua kehm mehle etoono efung, efungfu behre behre, abalimajom kehm rodo elkohl atahm ni Jehova.  
\v 13 Abalimajom na asehma, ba fili ntang esehma gbo mbang, jo jen jo wor atang, go mbuksong nyi elkohl atahm ni Jehova. Nsoja nyehko gbo bo mbang, nyehka jo toono elkohl atahm ni Jehova. Abalimajom soro asi jo wor atang ngare kpe kpe.  
\v 14 Go nfung ebal, bo jene sennge ejahbe nkpel anyehng, bo kpee feere song rehng go ebo edi erekekv. Ano wo bo limi no, go nfung na erakera.  
\v 15 Go efung bi biingi nfung esehma, bo nyahme efungfu atv atv, jen sennge ejahbe jio ana bo jo kono ellimi. Sehngem re efung bia bi bo jene sennge ejahbe nkpel esehma.  
\v 16 Eji ma biingi nkpel esehma nyi bo ma jen sennge ejahbe efung bia, ngare nyi abalimajom ma wor atang nya sahb wˈwahre, Josua kehm kake ane elkahn re, <<Raben! Tibre Jehova ma-n ka ejahbe jia!  
\v 17 Ḿ bahke rannge ejahbe jia kpee\f + \fr 6:17 \ft Ellum Hibru nia lohngo re elfaake ane a nsol a nsol kpee ka Jehova go mbang nyi bo bahke rannge afii jahmfi ka Jehova\f*, a ejum ajehng ajehng ji li go atahng. Sehngem Rehab ji li nne asˈsa, a ane kpee ba li go ege a nlaaga ba bahke sake, tibre á behre ane ba weele song nyehn ejahbe ba e tumu no.  
\v 18 Kana lak abo go ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo bahke rannge kpee, eji ń lꞌkꞌko elrannge ba ka elnahne tib ano. Ń lꞌlak abo bahke koko abꞌbi a afemfem ba kak edi erekekv.  
\v 19 Ejum ajehng ajehng ji bo limi go asilva a agul, a abrons, a akuungu li nsol nyi li saang ka Jehova. Nsol nyio kpee bo bahke koko song bum go etahk ji bo kpo kuuru nsol Jehova.  
\v 20 Eji bo woro atang nyao, ane kehm biiki, eji atang wahle no, ane kehm rabe wahre wahre, ekahme kehm soro gbo. Nnenlum awohng awohng kehm gehre yel songo songo ejahbe jio, ano wo bo ko ejahbe jio.  
\v 21 Bo yake ejahbe jio kpee ka Jehova, fere ko akahngkahng rannge nsol kpee nyi li go elkpin ana aneblum, anebkal, ba nse a ba nkul, go adahmagbudu, ejoro, a ebvankang.  
\v 22 Josua kehm tongo aneblum abal bao ba weele song nyehn ejahbe re, <<Songen go etahk nnenkal asˈsa noo, wahn song yehk-e, a ane ebe kpee, ana ń nyame no tong-e.  
\v 23 Ano wo njangkun ebal nyio, bo ji song weele nyehn ejahbe, kehm song yel yehke Rehab, nde, nnyehn, abonanyehn ba nlum a ba nkal, a ane kpee ba li a ne. Bo yehke ebangenahb eje kpee song bum edi ji li kohlo edi erekekv ji anebe Isreel.  
\v 24 Owo anebe Isreel kehm jahme ejahbe jio kpee fi, a nsol kpee nyi jolo go atahng. Wo bo kpu asilva, agul, a nsol nyi bo ko abrons go akuungu lim, song kak go etahk ji bo kpo kuuru nsol nyi Jehova.  
\v 25 Wo Josua yake Rehab nnenkal asꞌsa, a ebangenahb eje, go ane kpee ba jolo ka-e, á wulem bo, tibre á behre ajangkun nya Josua tumu re bo weele song nyehn Jeriko. Á lene go ellong ni anebe Isreel tete tub lela.  
\v 26 Ngare nyio Josua kehm nyame ko nwongo re: Go esamahr bi Jehova nne awohng awohng no lꞌgare re á tuungu ejahbe Jeriko jia si nkuk a ne: Re á bum nnahb ekahme, agbokambang a mmon ewe no nlum bahke kpoko; re á lim eti mbu, nkahla mmon ewe no nlum bahke kpoko.  
\v 27 Jehova jolo a Josua, elgahm ene yerre na yerre go ejahbe jio kpee. 
\c 7  
\s1 Aka nya Ekan Limi No 
\p  
\v 1 Wo anebe Isreel taamem bum ntahm nyi jolo re bo rannge nsol kpee go Jeriko. Ekan ji mmon no Kami, ji mmon no Jimri ji mmon no Jera, ji lohng go etˈtohngo ji Juda. Á rodo abon nsol o. Owo Jehova kehm rake atahng a anebe Isreel.  
\v 2 Josua kehm tumu ane o Jeriko re bo song go Eai, ji li kohlo Bet-Aven, ji li go ero nfam nyi Betel. Á kehm tongo bo re, <<Weelen song nyehn erohko ejahbe.>> Owo aneblum bao kehm tahme, fere song weele nyehn Eai.  
\v 3 Eji bo feere no ba kpiri Josua, bo kehm-e tongo re, <<Nsoja kpee sang bahke jeke song nok a Eai. Tum ane atahltahl nkpel elon, afi ane atahltahl nkpel esehma, a ane atahl awubu, bo song ko ejahbe jio. Ka gbiingi ane kpee, tibre li abon amohk ane abik abik go ejahbe jio.>>  
\v 4 Bo kehm tumu ane atahltahl nkpel esehma a ane atahl awubu, anebe Eai ga bo kpee,  
\v 5 bo fere wul eltahl nne elku, a nne awohng. Aneblum Eai kame anebe Isreel bomo go eti mbu tete rehng go adi nya bo kpo wa atal, fere wul bo go agbunggbung. Eji jolo ano eko tane anebe Isreel efung bia, ntim woono bo go elfahle, fere jol ana alahb.  
\v 6 Owo Josua, kehm yare nsol ebjing enye, gbo kohk asamahr go ndi, go mbuksong elkohl atahm ni Jehova, sa o tete elgung. Ano wo anebkul ba Isreel tob lim, kpu ebtohko wohngo elbo go ebo esi.  
\v 7 Josua kehm bungu re, <<O Ntubesi Jehova, jenji wahng ka a tohk kˈko ane baa ba siiri aya ma Jodan, re wo ba yak-r kak abo anebe Amor re bo wul-r? Jol nobo e sa sa go egbuk aya Jodan jehko!  
\v 8 Ntubesi, anv m bahke bungu rejen, eji anebekv ma kam anebe Isreel?.  
\v 9 Anebe Kenan, a ane bako ba li go edi jia bahke wuku bade ejum jia, bo bahke ba senng-r kak, fere wul-r, fvvdv mbing enyahre go njini. Ejum ajii a bahke limi tib go ega egburu mbing?>>  
\v 10 Owo Jehova kehm tongo Josua re, <<Mehl yiimi! Nˈnan a nong ana, esamahr eba go ndi?  
\v 11 Anebe Isreel eblim abiafem, bob soodo egbanngalung ji n jehke ntahm ka bo re bo bum. Bob rod nsol nyindiki nyi n tongo bo re bo rannge; bob v, fere rod behr go ebo a nsol, bob kim afahnge.  
\v 12 Ano wo wahnge anebe Isreel lˈkˈma yiimi a anebekv ebo. Bob sennge ajahm be, anv, wahn ebyehke mbang elrannge. N nehm ma kpe jol anahne tete ń rannge nsol nyi li egahne ellong nya li ka-n re wahn rannge.  
\v 13 <<Mehl! wo song nange ane. Tong bo re, <Bo nange elbo, toobo ebjing bi behna; Jia ji Jehova Esowo bi Isreel kpˈbungu: Isreel go egahne ellong wahn ebbehr ejum ji n tong-n re wahn rannge. Ń nehm ma kpe tiki yiimi a anebekv tete ń yehke nsol nyio egahne ellong.  
\v 14 << <Go efungfu, ḿ bahke lohngo ba etˈtohngo etˈtohngo; etˈtohngo ji Jehova bahke yehke, bahke lohngo ba esi ejahbe esi ejahbe; esi ejahbe ji Jehova bahke yehke bahke lohngo ba ebangenahb ebangenahb; ebangenahb ji Jehova bahke yehke, bahke lohngo ba nnenlum awohng awohng.  
\v 15 Nnenlum no bo lˈkpiri nsol nyi jolo re bo rannge go ege ebo, bo bahk-e fehke go agun, a ejum ajehng ajehng ji á kpi no, tibre yebgbo ntahm nyi Jehova, fvfo yeblim ejum esono go Isreel.> >>  
\v 16 Etoono efungfu atv atv Josua limi Isreel bo lohng etˈtohngo etˈtohngo, etˈtohngo ji Juda ji bo yehke no.  
\v 17 Asi ajahbe nya Juda kehm lohngo ba, anebe Jera ba gbo tub bo. Eji anebe Jera lohngo ebangenahb ebangenahb, gbo tub ebangnahb nyi Jimri.  
\v 18 Joshua kehm tongo ebangenahb ji Jimri re bo lohng nnenlum awohng awohng, kehm gboko tub Ekan mmon no Kami, ji mmon no Jimri, ji mmon no Jera, á lohng go etˈtohngo ji Juda.  
\v 19 Josua kehm tongo Ekan re, <<Ekan mmon ewame, ka Jehova ellub, Esowo Isreel, wo fere jo tehk-e. Tong-m ji a ma lim; kam-a tiki behr.>>  
\v 20 Owo Ekan kehm faange re, <<Etingitingi ji, me n lim abiafem bada Jehova Esowo bi Isreel. Ejum ji a, ji m ma lim:  
\v 21 Eji n nyehne nnobo nobo ekpawobo ji bo limi go Babilon, a ekpohko asilva atahl awubu, a ebahk agul jolo ana mmona nsob, ellubu ene jolo ejang ekilo, kor-m sehng, n kehm dake. Nsol nyia kpee nyia behr go atahng ndi go egame ebehre, akpohko asilva wob nla nsol nyio.  
\v 22 Josua kehm tumu atiingi etib, bo be song rehng ebehre, song nyehn behr go ege ebehre, a akpohko asilva nyao wob go nla nsol nyio.  
\v 23 Bo yehke nsol nyio go ebehre, ko ba goji Josua, go esamahr bi Isreel kpee. Bo rod yale gbuul go esamahr bi Jehova.  
\v 24 Owo Josua , a Isreel kpee kehm rodo Ekan mmon no Jera, a asilva akpohko nyao, a ebahk agul ji jolo ana mmon a nsob, a abon ebe ba nlum a ba nkal, a efong ebe, ebvankang, ejoro, ebehre eje, a ejum ajehng ajehng ji á bele no, tahm a nya go edamme ji Ako.  
\v 25 Josua kehm bahbe Ekan re, <<Jenji wahnge a ma ko ntong nyia ba kun-r esi? Jehova bahk-a kunu ntong lela.>> Owo anebe Isreel kpee kehm-e tuubu atal, bo tob tuubu ane ebe bako atal, fere jahm bo fi.  
\v 26 Bo kpu atal bul-e luk ebim, nya sa o tete rehng lela. Egburu erakatahng ji Jehova kehm feere go ndi. Owo wahnge bo lungu edamme jio re, edamme Ako\f + \fr 7:26 \ft Edamme ji Ako go ejahbe ji Hibru lohngo re edamme atongtong \f* wuku wuku. 
\c 8  
\s1 Anebe Isreel ga Eai 
\p  
\v 1 Owo Jehova kehm tongo Josua re, <<Ka kpe fahl, jol eltim ki-a woono. Rod nsoja kpee a na, wo song nok a Eai. Tib m ma-a kak ntula Eai go ega ebo, ane ebe, ejahbe eje, a ndi enye.  
\v 2 A bahke limi Eai a ntula bo, ana a limi Jeriko a ntula bo, elyaange ni bahke jolo a, ḿ bahke kpuku nsol nyi ḿ bahke dake a atohkondi ebo ka elnahne. Song noongen, go ebo ajahm ntahk.>>  
\v 3 Owo Josua a nsoja kpee kehm mehle re bo song nok a Eai. Á jake nsoja enye atahltahl nkpel atahl ara, a nkpel elku(30,000) nyi kpo sahb nˈnok nta, fere tum bo ngare atv,  
\v 4 a elkahn nia re: <<Wuungen atung nˈnob. Tumen ane bo song noongo go ebo ajahm ntahk. Kana je fee go njahm ntahk, wahn kpee jolen wake wake wahn jo sik.  
\v 5 Me, a ane ba li aname bahke song bohko ejahbe ebta, aneblum lˈlohng jo kam-r ana bo limi nyanjehle, e bahke jo be bo.  
\v 6 Bo bahk-r kame je fee tete e were bo yehke go ejahbe, wo bo bahke bungu re, <Bo kp-r beke ana bo be no nyanjehle.> Wo e lˈbe feere njahm,  
\v 7 owo ḿ bahke mehle adi nya ń nong no, song ko ejahbe. Jehova Esowo ebahne, bahk-n kake ejahbe jia go egahna abo.  
\v 8 Ngare nyi ń lˈko ejahbe jia, kaken agun jahm fi. Limen ji Jehova ma ka elkahn. Nyehnen; m ma-n ka elkahn.>>  
\v 9 Josua kehm song tv bo, bo kehm mehle atv mao song rehng adi elnoongo, go elka elka ni Betel a Eai, feere go erede bi Eai. Josua kange atv mao go ellong ane.  
\v 10 Efungfu behre behre etoono efung, Josua kehm mehle a ane ba be, ye, a anebkul Isreel gbo bo mbang asongo go Eai.  
\v 11 Nsoja kpee nyi jolo a ne jene asongo go ajahbe, song rehng go mbuksong ejahbe. Bo song limi edi erekekv ebo go ejang ebobkal bi Eai, edamme jolo go ebo elka, a ejahbe jio.  
\v 12 Josua rodo ejum ane atahltahl nkpel ewubbal, a ane atahl awubu re bo song noongo go elka elka ni Betel a Eai, feere erede bio bi ejahbe.  
\v 13 Bo limi nsoja song yiimi go ebo adi, bo jio kpee ji jolo edi erekekv feere go ejang ebobkal bi ejahbe, bo ji noongo no jolo ejang erede bi ejahbe. Atv mao Josua song yele go edamme.  
\v 14 Eji ntula Eai nyehne nsoja nyi Isreel, ye a aneblum kpee ba li ejahbe jio kehm mehle elwaare efungfu behre behre re bo nok a anebe Isreel edi ji li kohlo Araba. Wo á kahnem re bob noongo go ebo ajahm ntahk.  
\v 15 Josua a anebe Isreel kpee yake elbo jo be go ebo esamahr feere njahm njahm, bo jo be asongo go elka emahng.  
\v 16 Bo kehm lungu aneblum kpee go Eai re bo lohng ba kam anebe Isreel. Elkame ni bo jo kam Josua, ano wo nsoja nyi Isreel were bo yehke go ejahbe.  
\v 17 Nnenlum awohng awohng kpeem sa go Eai, afi go Betel no ki lohng jo kam anebe Isreel, bo lohngo ejahbe sa nnehme nehme lohng jo kam anebe Isreel.  
\v 18 Owo Jehova kehm tongo Josua re, <<Ton elkong ni wob-a go ebo tv go Eai, tib go ega ebo wo m bahk-a kake ejahbe jio.>> Ano wo Josua tono elkong ene tv go Eai.  
\v 19 Tvtv ana Josua tono elkong nia, ane ba noongo go ekul, kehm lohngo elwaare abahl abahl go adi nya bo noongo no asongo mbuksong mbuksong. Bo yele go ejahbe, song ko ejahbe jio, fere jahm elwaare go agun.  
\v 20 Aneblum ba Eai keebe kan go njahm me, bo nyehne atˈtohk go ejahbe ma rehng wahre wahre go elbung, bo kpeem bel edi ji bo bahke kpe be tahm. Tib anebe Isreel ba jo be njahm njahm yel go emahng, ebfeere kpˈnoko a ane ba kpi bo kam.  
\v 21 Eji Josua a anebe Isreel kpee nyehne re ane ba noongo go ajahm ntahk, ebsong yel ko ejahbe, fere nyehn atˈtohk kpˈlohngo go ejahbe, bo kehm sennge fere jo nok a aneblum Eai.  
\v 22 Ane ba noongo no, eji bo song yel ejahbe jahm fi, kehm feere lohng ba kehme elnoko a anebe Eai, bo sa go elka elka, anebe Isreel go esi ebbal ebbal, Isreel kehm wulu bo jol nnene saam go elkpin, jol nnene bo we-e bobem ana nju.  
\v 23 Wo ntula Eai wo bo bob-e no bum go elkpin, fere ko-e ba ka Josua.  
\v 24 Eji anebe Isreel ma wul ane kpee ba bo jo kam go ekulugbe a ekpawumu emahng ,bo ji bo kame bo song rehng, eji bo ma wul nne awohng awohng ebo go ekahngkahng, Isreel kpee kehm feere go Eai song wul erik ane ji jolo go atahng ejahbe.  
\v 25 Aneblum a anebkal ba bo wulu efung bio jolo ane atahltahl, eltahl a nkpel ewubu (12,000) bo kpee ba lene go Eai.  
\v 26 Josua tikem feere ebo bi jabbe elkong go ndi bi á tono go ero, tete bo wul nne awohng awohng no lene go Eai.  
\v 27 Anebe Isreel dˈdaa nsol kpee go ejahbe jia bum elbo, ana ntohkondi, a nsol afang ebo, jang jang ana Jehova tubu Josua elle.  
\v 28 Ano wo Josua jahme Eai go agun fi kpee, fere lim ejahbe jio fere sa ana ebimbim nkahlkahl. Sa ano nnehme nehme tete rehng efung bia.  
\v 29 Josua kehm rodo ntula Eai kahn-e ekehd go eti, á sa tokko eti tete elgung. Ngare nyi njul ma lahm Josua kehm tongo bo re, bo fannge ngubjing go eti, rod-e song tahnge tub go ndi go eti mbu jio ji ejahbe. Bo kpu atal song bul-e luk ebim li o tete tub bi lela. 
\s1 Anebe Isreel Tuungu Egbanngalung Ji Jehova Lim Go Ewong Ji Ebal 
\p  
\v 30 Josua kehm limi egudu njom ka Jehova Esowo bi Isreel, go ewong ji Ebal,  
\v 31 ano wo Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova tongo anebe Isreel. Á limi ana bo nyono go nwer atahm nyi Mosis, egudu njom ji bo ki kiimi atal, nya bo ki ko ekuungu soongo. Egudu jio wo bo limi ajom nya bo kpo jahm fi, a ajom nyao nya elkoono ka Jehova.  
\v 32 O, esamahr bi anebe Isreel Josua fiki atahm nya Mosis go atal, nyao nya Mosis nyono ka bo.  
\v 33 Isreel kpee, ajenne, afono ejahbe, anebkul ebo, atubesi nsoja, a abalamalam, bo yiimi ejang ebbal ebbal bi elkohl atahm ni Jehova, jo seenge ane ba solo no, abalimajom, bo ji li anebe Levi. Egom ane jehko yiimi go mbuksong ewong ji Garisim, bo jehko yiimi go mbuksong ewong ji Ebal, ana Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova ma tohko tong bo, eji á ka bo elle ni elfuulu abone Isreel.  
\v 34 Eji ma jol ano, Josua kehm ba lung alum atahm nya Jehova kpee, nya elfuulu, a nya elsu, ful ful fuul ana Mosis yeele go nwer atahm.  
\v 35 Ellum anehng anehng jolem ni Mosis ka elkahn, ni Josua ki lung go ka anebe Isreel kpee, budu anebkal, abonse, a ajenne ajenne nya lene go ebo ellong. 
\c 9  
\s1 Anebe Gibion Nehme Anebe Isreel 
\p  
\v 1 Eji atul bao ba li feere erede bi aya Jodan wuku bade nsol nyia, ntula Hid, Amor, Kenan, a no Peres, a no Hiv, a no Jebus, bo ji lene go edi awong awong nya li feere erede, agbung gbung awong go erede nfam, fvfo go nkpe agburu aya ma a lꞌkꞌma nyehn egbuk jehko, tete rehng go Lebanon,  
\v 2 bo bungu bum nnyo amehng re bo ba nok a Josua a anebe Isreel.  
\v 3 Wo eji anebe Gibion wuku ji Josua ma lim anebe Jeriko, a Eai,  
\v 4 anebe Gibion kehm toobo re bo nehm anebe Isreel, eji bo lˈtahre elbo. Bo tahme ana ane ba bo tumu bo, bo kake nsol go agbajake abam rod gbade ebvankang ebo, a ayahbe nya ma kul, bo ma baade adi adi.  
\v 5 Bo kake agbajake nsol go bo agubjing, a akˈkulu akpaketa go akpade nya bo ma baade adi adi. Bo rodo akpawake abred nya ma tub amvmv.  
\v 6 Bo kehm song kpiri Josua go edi erekekv ji Gilgal, bo kehm tongo Josua a anebe Isreel re, <<E lohng mbang alab. Koon nwongo anahre.>>  
\v 7 Anebe Isreel kehm bahbe anebe Hiv re, <<Anv, Bahke ma jol re ń lohng a kpidi kpidi, bahke limi renan e bahk kehm koko nwongo anahne?>>  
\v 8 Bo kehm bungu tong Josua re, <<Wahr aloketum ebahne ba.>> Josua kehm bahb bo re, “Wahn ane a baa? Ń lohng gan ba?”  
\v 9 Bo kehm bungu re, <<E lohng fee ba. Wahr ebwuk bade egburu nsahm nyi Jehova Esowo ebahne. Wahr ebwuk aka bada ne: nsol kpee nyi á limi go Ijib,  
\v 10 wahr ebtob wuk bade ana á limi atul abal ba anebe Amor, bo ji jolo feere ero nfam bio bi aya ma Jodan. Sihon ntul no Hesbon, a Og ntul no Basan, ye ji kuumu go Astarod.  
\v 11 Anebkul ebahre, a ane ba lene go egahre ejahbe tong-r re, <<Tooben ebjing wahn mehl eljen song kpiri anebe Israel fere tong bo re, <<Wahr aloketum ebahne ba, Koon nwongo anahre.>> >  
\v 12 Abred enyahre nyaa jolo elfu elfu, eji e gbade elkpang go etahk, efung bi e mehle eljen kpꞌbake go egahne. Wo anv ebwuumu, fere tub amvmv.  
\v 13 Ayahbe enyahre nyaa jolo nfenfe, anv, ebkul, fere bahnge. Nsol ebjing enyahre nyia a akpaketa jolo nfenfe nfenfe, anv ebkpo alahb fere jak, tib go alaaba mbang nyi e lohng abake.  
\v 14 Anebe Isreel kehm ba feede nsol ebo kpee, jol bo bahbem Jehova.  
\v 15 Owo Josua kehm limi elkoono fere ko nwongo a bo, re bo nehm wul bo. Anebkul nfam taame tv, fere ko nwongo.  
\v 16 Eji ma biingi nfung era nyi anebe Isreel limi elkoono fere ko nwongo a anebe Gibion, anebe Isreel kehm ba wuk re ane baa lene kpidi kpidi kohlo bo, bo lenem fee.  
\v 17 Owo anebe Isreel kehm mehle asongo, go nfung era bo kehm song rehng go ebo ajahbe: Gibion, Kefira, Biirot, a Kiriad Jearim.  
\v 18 Anebe Isreel nokem a bo, tibre atubesi anebe Isreel ebko nwongo a bo go mbing nyi Jehova, Esowo bi Isreel. Anebe Isreel kpee kehme elmemme bade atubesi ebo,  
\v 19 owo atubesi anebe Isreel kpee kehm faange bo re, <<Wahr ebko nwongo abo go esamahr bi Jehova, Esowo bi Isreel, e nehm ma lak bo abo anv.  
\v 20 Ejum ji a, ji e bahke bo lim: Nong wahr yaken bo, bo jol go elkpin, eji erem lˈkˈgbo tub-r e lˈgbo go nwongo nyi e ma ko a bo.>>  
\v 21 Atubesi anebe Isreel kehm bungu re, <<Nong bo jol go elkpin, jo gbakke nkun, fere jo tuk alahb ka ejahbe kpee. Go mbang nyio ji atubesi bungu no bade abo, bo lꞌlim.  
\v 22 Owo Josua kehm lungu anebe Gibion, kehm bungu a bo re, <<Jenji wahng ka ń kehm ba nehm-r, eji ń tong-r re, <E lohng fee,> na nyehne ga ń lohko lene a kpidi kpidi?”  
\v 23 Wahn ebbel elsu: Bomo anv asongo, ḿ bahke jo lok-r ana abarake nkun, fere jol abatukalahb ka go etahk Esowo ebame.>>  
\v 24 Bo kehm faange re, <<Wahr aloeltum eba e limi jia, tibre bo tong-r re, <<Bo tongo alokeltum eba gbul gbul gbuul re, Jehova Esowo bi Isreel ebtong Mosis nloketum ewe re, á ka-n ndi nyia kpee, fere wul nne awohng awohng no lene o egahne esamahr. Wo e bele elfahle ni nkpin enyahre tib esi ejahne, owo wanhge e limi ejum jia.  
\v 25 Anv e li go egahna abo. Lim-r ejum ajehng ajehng ji kpˈnobo a ji li nseenge go egahne esamahr.  
\v 26 Ano wo Josua tahre bo go abo nya anebe Isreel, fvfo anebe Isreel wulem nne Gibion awohng awohng.  
\v 27 Go efung bio Josua limi anebe Gibion bo jol abarake nkun, a abatukalahb ka anebe Isreel kpee, a edi egudu njom ji Jehova, edi jio ji Jehova bahke yehke re bo si. Ano wo bo jo lim tete sik lela. 
\c 10  
\s1 Anebe Isreel Ga Anebe Amor 
\p  
\v 1 Anv eji Adoni-Jedek ntula Jeusalem wuku re Josua ebko Eai, fere rannge ejahbe jio kpee, yeblim Eai a ntula bo ana á limi Jeriko a ntula bo, fvfo ana anebe Gibion ma lim elkoono a anebe Isreel, bobfere jol kohlo bo.  
\v 2 Ntul noa, a ane ebe bele elfahle gbalee eji bo wuku nsol ana nyia, tibre Gibion jolo egburu ejahbe ji kpi ekpunu, jolo ajahbe etul; gbale sehnge Eai. Aneblum ebo kpee jolo abanokebta ba nno a nno.  
\v 3 Owo Adoni-Jedek ntula Jeusalem kehm lungu Hoham ntula Hebron, Piram ntula Jamud, Jafia ntula Lakis, Debir ntula Eglon, kehm kpake njahm a bo.  
\v 4 Á kehm tongo bo re, <<Baan, wahn ba tob-m nok a Gibion, tibre boblim elkoono a Josua, a anebe Isreel.>>  
\v 5 Owo atul baa na alon ba anebe Amor, atul ba Jeusalem, Hebron, Jamud, Lakis, Eglon kehm kono asi. Bo kpee kehm mehle, a nsoja ebo, song rod ebo ebta a anebe Gibion kehme elnoko a bo.  
\v 6 Anebe Gibion kehm tumu ellum tv Josua go edi erekekv ji Gilgal: <<Kana wahr yake, wahr aloketum ebahne ba. Baan ga elwaare, wahn ba tahr-r. Kak-r ebo, tibre atul baa ba anebe Amor bo jio ji kun go ejahbe awong ebkpa njahm re bo ba nok anahre.>>  
\v 7 Wo Josua kehm mehle go Gilgal a nsoja enye kpee, nyi semme a atahntahn ane kpee ba kpo sahb nˈnok ebta.  
\v 8 Jehova kehm bungu tong Josua re, <<Ka tiki bel elfahle bada bo; Me n faake bo kak-a go ebo. Jol nnene limm no bahk-a ma yiimi go abo.>>  
\v 9 Eji Josua ma jen atv atv mao, bomo go Gilgal asongo, Josua song gbede nsoja Amor eji bo ki kahn.  
\v 10 Jehova limi amahr bil bo go esamahr anebe Isreel, Isreel ga bo go egburu elgake go Gibion. Isreel soro asi jo kam bo mbang mbang nyio nyi Bet Horon, bo wulu bo gbalee mbang mbang nyio nyi Ajeka abola Makkeda.  
\v 11 Ana bo kpˈbeke go esamahr bi Isreel go mbang nyi lohngo go Bet-Horon asongo go Ajeka, Jehova kehm nake elahb atal go elbung wul ane gbalee. Ba kpo go elahb atal ba ga gbal sehnge ba anebe Isreel wulu akahngkahng.  
\v 12 Efung bi Jehova faake anebe Amor kak anebe Isreel go abo, Josua bungu tong Jehova go esamahr bi Isreel re, <<Njul sa yiimi go ero bi Gibion, ebareka sa yiimi o, ero edamme ji Aijalon.>>  
\v 13 Ano wo njul sa no yiimi, wo ebareka sa yiimi, tete anebe Isreel nok ga anebekv ebo, ana bo nyono go Nwer nyi Jasa. Njul sa yiimi go elka elka ni elbung, lahmem ejum efung kohro kohro.  
\v 14 Efung ana efung bio ka jˈjol, bomo efung bio efung ana bio ka kpe tiki jol, efung bi Jehova wuungu atung go ellum ni nne. Etingitingi Jehova jo nˈnok ka Isreel!  
\v 15 Owo Josua kehm feere a nsoja enye kehnge go edi erekekv ji Gilgal. 
\s1 Josua Wulu Atul Alon Ba Anebe Amor 
\p  
\v 16 Ngare nyia atul baa na alon ebbe song biiri go nkpaltal nyi li go Makkeda.  
\v 17 Wo eji bo ba tong Josua re bobnyehn atul baa na alon behr go nkpaltal nyi li go Makkeda,  
\v 18 á kehm bungu tong bo re, “Banngen, agburu atal wahn sahd go nkpaltal nyio, wahn fere yehke ane bum jo baabe.  
\v 19 Kana rahke! Kamen anebekv ebahne, jo noken toono bo go njahm, kana taame bo yel go ebo ejahbe, tibre Jehova Esowo ebahne, ebfaake bo kak-n go ebo.  
\v 20 Ano wo Josua a nsoja nyi Isreel soro asi jo wul bo, sa na mmobsake, bo ji male be song yel go ebo ajahbe nya bo si akahme sennge kak.  
\v 21 Nsoja nyi Isreel kpee feere kehnge, nnene ejum we limem, ba rehng goji Josua edi erekekv, ngo Makkeda, , jol nnene bungem ebi ellum anehng anehng bada anebe Isreel.  
\v 22 Josua kehm bungu tong bo re, <<Lennge nnyo nkpaltal nyio wahn yehke atul alon bao ba ka-m.>>  
\v 23 Owo bo kehm yehke atul alon bao go nkpaltal, ntul no Jeusalem, Hebron, Jamod, Lakis, a Eglon.  
\v 24 Eji bo ma ko atul bao ba ka Josua, á kehm lungu nsoja Isreel kpee kehm bungu tong atubesi nsoja ba ba a ne re, <<Baan, wahn ba rod akpade enyahne kunu atul baa go bo amel. Owo bo kehm bake ba kunu bo akpade go ebo amel>>  
\v 25 Josua kehm bungu tong bo re, <<Kana fahl; ntim enyahne ki-n woono. Yiimi tˈtahne, wahn bel esahbeltim. Elkohn ejum ana jia ji Jehova bahke limi anebekv ebahne kpee ba ḿ bahke noko a bo.>>  
\v 26 Josua kehm wulu atul alon bao kpee, rod bo kpake go nti na elon tete ngare elgung.  
\v 27 Eji njul ma lahm, Josua kehm kake bo elkahn re bo song fono bo go nti, bo kehm song fono bo, song ro bo kak go nkpaltal nyi bo biiri no. Go nnyo nkpaltal nyio bo bannge agburu atal bum o, nyaa luk o tete rehng lela. 
\s1 Josua Kpe Rannge Ajahbe Anebe Amor Gbalee 
\p  
\v 28 Efung bio Josua rannge ejahbe Makkeda kpee, fere wul ntula bo, a nne awohng awohng no li go ejahbe jio. Nnene á yakem no sa go elkpin. Á limi ntula Makkeda , ana á limi ntula Jeriko.  
\v 29 Josua kehm mehle a anebe Isreel go Makkeda song rehng go Libna song nok a bo.  
\v 30 Jehova tob faake ejahbe jia a ntula bo kak Isreel go ebo. Josua koo ekahngkahng rannge ejahbe jio, fere wul nne awohng awohng. Nnene á yakem no sa go elkpin o. Á limi ntula a bo ana á limi ntula Jeriko.  
\v 31 Josua kehm kpe sehng o Libna, a Isreel kpee song rehng go Lakis song sennge bo, nok a bo.  
\v 32 Jehova faake Lakis kak Isreel go ebo, ano wo Josua ga ejahbe jia etoono efung. Ejahbe jia, a nne awohng awohng no jolo o, á wulu bo ekahngkahng jangjang ana á limi go Libna.  
\v 33 Gana Horam ntula Gejer ebba re á ba tob Lakis, wo Josua nok ga-e a nsoja enye, tete nnene kpeem jol no sa go elkpin.  
\v 34 Owo Josua, a anebe Isreel kpee kehm mehle a ne o Lakis, asongo go Eglon; song sennge bo, nok a bo.  
\v 35 Bo bobo ejahbe jia efung bˈnehm bi bo bomo elnoko a bo, wul bo go akahngkahng, fere rannge nne awohng awohng ana bo limi go Lakis.  
\v 36 Owo Josua a Isreel kpee kehm mehle go Eglon song rehng go Hebron, song nok a bo.  
\v 37 Bo ko ejahbe jio, fere wul bo go akahngkahng, a ntula bo, a abon ajahbe ebo, a nne awohng awohng no lene o. Nnene bo yakem no sa elkpin. Ana bo limi Eglon, bo tob rannge Hebron kpee a nne awohng awohng go atahng.  
\v 38 Wo Josua a anebe Isreel kpee mehle a ne, sennge song nok a Debir.  
\v 39 Bo ko ejahbe jia, a ntula bo, a abon ajahbe ba nse, fere wul bo go akahngkahng. Bo rannge nne awohng awohng no li o kpee. Nnene bo yakem no sa go elkpin. Bo rannge Debir a ntula bo, jang jang ana bo rannge Libna a ntula bo, fvfo ana bo limi Hebron.  
\v 40 Ana wo Josua ga ajahbe nyaa kpee go erohko jia, a edi awong awong, emahng ji ejang eboblum, a abangenahb awong nya erede nfam, a akpe kpe agburu awong, a atul ebo kpee. Nnene á yakem no sa go elkpin. Josua wulu, ejum ajehng ajehng kpo v elv, jang jang ana Jehova Esowo bi Isreel ka-e elkahn.  
\v 41 Josua wulu bo, bomo go Kedes Bania tete song rehng go Gaja, sehng o rehng go arohko kpee nya Goseen tete rehng go Gibion.  
\v 42 Atul baa kpee, a ndi abo, Josua mehle nok a bo go ellohngo anehng ni á mehle ebta a bo, tibre Jehova Esowo bi Isreel, noko ka Isreel.  
\v 43 Owo Josua kehm feere kehnge a Isreel kpee go edi erekekv ji Gilgal. 
\c 11  
\s1 Anebe Isreel Noko Ga Atul Ba Ejang Ebobkal Nfam 
\p  
\v 1 Eji Jabin ntula Hajo wuku bada esehnge ebta bi anebe Isreel, á kehm tumu ellum tv Jobab ntula Madon, a atul ba Simron a Akisaf,  
\v 2 á tob tumu tv atul bako ba li li ejang ebobkal ero awong, fere tob tumu tv atul ba Araba ji li ejang eboblum bi Kinered, a atul ba li go abangenahb awong nya li erede nfam, a bao ba li go Nafod Dor ji li feere erede nfam;  
\v 3 á tob tumu tv atul ba anebe Kenan, ero a erede nfam; a atul ba anebe Amor, Hid, Peres, Jebus ba li go edi awong awong; a atul ba anebe Hiv ba li go edamme ji Hemon ji li go elwo ni Mijipa.  
\v 4 Bo lohngo a nsoja ebo kpee, nlong anyˈnya, go amvtv akuungu gbalee. Egburu nlong nrur nsoja, bo ji ruru ana eriki bi nkpe aya.  
\v 5 Atul baa kpee ba ko nsoja ebo ba kono asi edi ajehng, bo ba limi edi ererkekv ebo go alahb ma Merom, re bo nok a anebe Isreel.  
\v 6 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Josua re, <<Kana bel elfahle anehng anehng bada bo. Behna ngare nyia, m bahke faake bo kak Isreel go abo, bo kpee bahke jolo akvne akvne. A bahke kiimi anyˈnya ebo alumlum ajahb kpade, wahn fere jamme amvtv akuungu ebo fi.>>  
\v 7 Owo Josua a nsoja enye kpee kehm ba gbehl bo kohlo alahb ma Merom, kehm noko a bo,  
\v 8 wo Jehova kehm yake bo kak Isreel go ebo. Bo ga bo, fere kehm kehme bo kam mbang mbang nyio nyi rehng go Egburu Sidon tete rehng go Misrefod Main, song rehng go edamme ji Mijipa go ero nfam, tete nnene kpeem sa no jolo go elkpin.  
\v 9 Josua limi bo ana Jehova tong-e no. Á kehm kiimi anyˈnya ebo alumlum ajahb kpade kpee, fere fi amvtv akuungu ebo.  
\v 10 Ngare nyia Josua feere njahm ba bob Hajo, fere wul ntula bo go ekahngkahng. Hajo jia ji tohko jol ntubesi ejahbe, ji ajahbe atul nyaa kpee.  
\v 11 Nne awohng awohng ejahbe jia bo wul-e go ekahngkahng, Isreel rannge bo kpee, jol ejum ajehng ajehng ji kpi elv, bo yakem sa. Josua jahme Hajo fi.  
\v 12 Josua ga ajahbe atul nyaa kpee, a atul ebo, fere wul bo akahngkahng. Á rannge bo kpee, ana Mosis nlokeltum Jehova ka bo elkahn.  
\v 13 Wo Isreel ejahbe ajehng ajehng bo jahmem fi ji bo si kunu abuntahk, sehngem re Hajo ji Josua jahme no fi.  
\v 14 Anebe Isreel da nsol nyi ajahbe nyaa kpee, a ntohkondi atohkondi ebo. Wo ane baa kpee, bo wulu bo go akahngkahng, tete bo rannge bo kpee, jol ejumjum saam ji bele elv.  
\v 15 Ana Jehova ka Mosis nlokeltum ewe elkahn, ano wo Mosis tob ka Josua elkahn, Josua limi kpee, ejumjum jolem ji Josua ki lim, go nsol kpee nyi Jehova ka Mosis elkahn re á lim. 
\s1 Adi ndi nya anebe Isreel noko ebta ko 
\p  
\v 16 Ano wo Josua noko ko ndi nyia kpee: edi awong awong, a awumwum adi nya li go ejang eboblum, a ndi nyi Goseen kpee, go abangenahb awong nya li go erede nfam, a edamme ji Araba, a agburu awong kpee nya li go Isreel, a abangenahb awong ebo,  
\v 17 bomo go ewong ji Halak ji li feere go Seya tete song rehng go Baal Gad ji li go edamme Lebanon nnahb egburu ewong nyi Hemon. Josua bobo atul ebo kpee, fere wul bo.  
\v 18 Josua noko ebta a atul bao ekidi sahb lˈlab.  
\v 19 Nnene limem elkoono a anebe Isreel, sehngem re anebe Hiv ba lene go Gibion ba ba, Isreel ga bo kpee go ebta.  
\v 20 Jehova antahng antahng wo limi re ntim ebo tahne, eji bo lˈyiimi abohng a Isreel, eji á lˈsehng o wul bo kpee, fere yehke bo jol ndon á beem, ana Jehova ka Mosis elkahn.  
\v 21 Ngare nyio Josua wulu etˈtohngo ji Anak kpee, bo ji lene go edi awong awong: Hebron, Debir, Anab, go edi awong awong kpee nya li go Juda, a edi awong awong nya li go Isreel. Josua wulu bo kpee, fere rannge ajahbe ebo kpee.  
\v 22 Go ndi nyi Isreel, nne awohng awohng no Anak saam, go Gaja, Gati, a Asdod wo wo abon amohk anebe Anak sa no.  
\v 23 Owo Josua kehm koko ndi kpee, jang jang ana Jehova tongo Mosis. Josua bake edi ndi jia ka anebe Isreel ebangenahb ebangenahb ana ejum elehkelkv. Owo ndi bele erekekv go nta anoko. 
\c 12  
\s1 Atul Ba Mosis Ga Go Ebta 
\p  
\v 1 A wo li Atul ba ndi nyia, ba anebe Isreel noko a bo, fere ga bo, fere taare adi ndi ebo go ero bi Jodan, bomo go edamme ji Anon rehng go egburu ewong ji Hemon, tob budu ero nfam bio bi Araba:  
\v 2 Sihon ntul no anebe Amor, ye ji kuumu go Hesbon. Á jo fili edi bomo go Aroe ji li nkpe edamme nyi Anon. Bomo go elka edaame, rehng go aya Jabok ma li nkonkon nyi anebe Amon. Ejang ejahbe ji Giled jolo budu o.  
\v 3 Á tob jo fili ero bio bi Araba bomo go aya ma Kinered tete rehng go agburu aya Araba ma li aya akang, song rehng go Bet-Jesimod, fere feere ejang eboblum, edamme jio ji Pisga.  
\v 4 Go ejang ndi bi Og ntula Basan, esˈkohro ntul no anebe Refa, ye ji jii jo fili Astarot abola Edrei.  
\v 5 Á fili edi bomo go ewong Hemon rehng go Saleka, Basan kpee tete rehng go nkonkon nyi anebe Gesur a Maaka, a ejang Giled rehng go nkonkon nyi Sihon ntula Hesbon.  
\v 6 Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova, a anebe Isreel ga bo. Wo Mosis faaka ndi ebo ka anebe Ruben, Gad, a ejang etˈtohngo ji anebe Manase, re jol ndi abo. 
\s1 Atul Ba Josua Ga Go ebta 
\p  
\v 7 Atul ba ndi nyia ba a, ba Josua a anebe Isreel noko a bo, fere ga bo, go ejang erede bi Jodan, bomo go Baal Gad ji li edamme ji Lebanon song rehng go ewong Halak ji li feere go Seir. Josua ka bo ndi atˈtohngo atˈtohngo ana ejum elehkelkv ebo.  
\v 8 Ndi nyi Josua bake no nya a; edi awong awong, a nya li go abangenahb awong erede nfam, Araba, a nkpale nkpale ewong, a elka emahng feere ejang eboblum - ndi nyio nyi anebe Hid, anebe Amor, anebe Kenan, anebe Pereji, anebe Hiv, a anebe Jebus:  
\v 9 ntula Jeriko, ntula Eai( ji li kohlo Betel)  
\v 10 ntula Jeusalem, ntula Hebron,  
\v 11 ntula Jamud, ntula Lakis,  
\v 12 ntula Eglon, a ntula Geja,  
\v 13 ntula Debir, ntula Geda,  
\v 14 ntula Homa, a ntula Arad,  
\v 15 ntula Libna, ntul Adulam,  
\v 16 ntula Makkeda, ntula Betel,  
\v 17 ntula Tapua, ntula Hefa,  
\v 18 ntula Afek, ntula Lasaron,  
\v 19 ntula Madon, ntula Hajo,  
\v 20 ntula Simron Meron, ntula Akisaf,  
\v 21 ntula Taanak, ntula Megido,  
\v 22 ntula Kedesh, ntula Joknam go Kamel,  
\v 23 ntula Dor ji jolo go Nafod Dor, ntula Goyim go Gilgal,  
\v 24 a ntula Tirja. Bo kpee jolo eltahl atul awubu, a ntul awohng. 
\c 13  
\s1 Adi Ndi Nya Ma Sa Re Bo nok Ko 
\p  
\v 1 Eji Josua ma sahb kˈkul, owo Jehova kehm-e tongo re, <<Anv wobsahb kˈkul, wo gana adi ndi nyaa kpeka li gbalee ka-n re wahn ko.  
\v 2 Adi ndi nya a, nya ma sa: Ajang ndi kpee nya anebe Filista a anebe Gesu:  
\v 3 bomo go aya ma Siho, ero bi Ijib, feere ndi nyi Ekron ejang ebobkal. Ndi nyia kpee jolo ndi nyi anebe Kenan: Adi ndi nya jolo ka atul na alon ba Filista nya a, Gaja, Asdod, Askelon, Gati, a Ekron. Ndi nyi anebe Avva;  
\v 4 bomo ejang eboblum, ndi kpee nyi anebe Kenan, bomo Ara ji anebe Sidon, sehng tete rehng go Afek, ejang bi anebe Amor,  
\v 5 edi jio ji anebe Gebal, a Lebanon kpee, nyi li ero nfam, bomo go Baal Gad ji erede egburu ewong Hemon tete rehng go Lebo Hamad.  
\v 6 Bade ane bao ba lene go ajahbe nya kun agburu awong, bomo go Lebanon tete rehng go Misrefod Maim, anebe Sidon bao kpee. Mefono antahng bahke kame bo yehke go esamahr anebe Isreel. Tiki nok wo ka anebe Isreel edi ndi jia ana ejum elehkelkv, ana n tong-a no,  
\v 7 fvfo bak ana ejum elehkelkv ka etˈtohngo na ebsehmwubu a ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase.>> 
\s1 Mbake Nyi Adi Ndi Nya Ero Bi Jodan 
\p  
\v 8 Ejang etˈtohngo Manase jehko, anebe Ruben, a anebe Gad, bobko ejum elehkelkv bo ji, Mosis ka bo go ero bi aya ma Jodan, Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova wo ka bo.  
\v 9 Ndi ebo bomo go Aroe, go nkpe nyi edamme Anon, bomo ejahbe ji li go elka edamme tete rehng go nwahre wahre edi ji li ebale ebale ji Medeba sehng o song rehng go Dibon,  
\v 10 fvfo ajahbe kpee nya ntula Amor no bo kpo lung-e re Sihon, ye ji jolo go Hesbon jo fili ane, tete rehng go nkonkon nyi anebe Amon.  
\v 11 Giled tob woomo go atahng, ejang bio bi Gesu, a Maaka, a ejang egburu ewong bi Hemon kpee, ndi Basan kpee tete rehng go Saleka,  
\v 12 a wo li edi ndi kpee ji ntula Og jo fili go Basan, ye ji kuumu go Astarot abola Edrei, á jolo esˈkohro ntul no anebe Refa. Mosis noko a bo, ga bo, fere ko ndi ebo.  
\v 13 Wo anebe Isreel Kamem anebe Gesu, a anebe Maaka, bo soro asi lene go ellong anebe Isreel tete tub bi lela. 
\s1 Elehkelkv Ji Anebe Levi 
\p  
\v 14 Wo Mosis Kaam etˈtohngo ji Levi edi ndi ajehng ajehng, eji jolo re ayare anyehng anyehng nya bo jo jahm na fi ka Jehova Esowo bi Isreel, nya nya jolo ejum elehkelkv ebo, ana Jehova nyame no tong bo. 
\s1 Edi ndi Ji Bo Ka Etˈtohngo Ji Ruben 
\p  
\v 15 Ana wo Mosis ka etˈtohngo ji Ruben edi ndi go ebangnahb ebangenahb:  
\v 16 Bomo Aroe ji li go nkahl nyi edamme ji Anon, fvfo bomo ejahbe ji wob go elka elka ni edamme, song rehng go nwahre wahre edi ji jolo ebal ebal ji li sehng go Medeba,  
\v 17 song rehng go Hesbon, a ajahbe nyaa nya li edi ebal ebal: Dibon, Bamod Baal, Bed Baal Meon,  
\v 18 Jahaji, Kedemot, Mefaat,  
\v 19 Kiriatayim,a Sibma, a Jeret Saha ji li go ewong ji li go edamme,  
\v 20 Bet-peor, agbung gbung nya ewong Pisga abola Bet-Jesimot,  
\v 21 budu ajahbe kpee nya li go awahre wahre adi nya li ebal ebal, a ajahbe kpee nya ntula Sihon jo fili. Sihon wo jolo ntul no anebe Amor, ye ji lene go Hesbon, Mosis wul-e wul budu a atul bako ba Media, ana ntula Evi, Rekem, Jur, Hur, Reba, atubesi baa jolo jo fili adi a ntula Sihon.  
\v 22 Anebe Isreel wulu Balam mmon no Beor go ekahngkahng, ye ji jolo nnea ntaane, budu ane ba bo wulu go ebta.  
\v 23 Nkonandi nyi etˈtohngo ji Ruben jolo nkpe nkpe nyi aya ma Jodan. Ajahbe, a abon ajahbe ba jolo a kpee jolo ejum elehkelkv ka etˈtohngo Ruben, ebangenahb ebangenahb. 
\s1 Edi Ndi Ji Bo Ka Etˈtohngo Ji Gad 
\p  
\v 24 Edi ndi ji a, ji Mosis ka etˈtohngo ji Gad ebangenahb abanganahb:  
\v 25 Edi ndi ji Jaje, a ajahbe kpee nya li Giled, a ejang nfam ji anebe Amon tete asongo go Aroer ji li kohlo Rabba,  
\v 26 fvfo bomo go Hesbon song rehng go Rama Mijipa, a Betonim, sehng go Mahanayim tete song rehng go edi ndi ji Debir,  
\v 27 Beth Aram, Bet-nimra, Sukot, a Jafon nya li go edamme, a erik ajahbe nya jolo go elwo ni ntula Sihon ji lene go Hesbon. Nseenge ebo jolo erede ajahbe nyao, sehnge go aya ma Jodan, sehng asongo tete rehng go edi ji agburu aya ma Kineret kohlo no.  
\v 28 Ajahbe nyaa a abon erik ajahbe ba jolo a kpee, jolo ejum elehkelkv ka etˈtohngo ji Gad, ebangenahb ebangenahb. 
\s1 Edi Ndi Ji Bo Ka Ejang Etˈtohngo Ji Manase 
\p  
\v 29 Edi ndi ji a ji Mosis kaa ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase. Ji lohngo re, á kaa ejang abon ba Manase, ebangenahb ebangenahb.  
\v 30 Ndi ebo bomo go Mahanayim, Basan kpee woomo atahng, adi kpee nya woomo ntula Og ji jolo go Basan go elwo, a nsi kpee nyi jolo go Jair, ji Basan, kpee jolo nsi atahl ara,  
\v 31 ejang ejahbe Giled, a Estarod abola Endreyi nya li ajahbe nya ntula Og jo fili, ye ji lene go Basan) . Nyaa kpee li ka etꞌtohngo ji Maki ji jolo mmona Manase, jolo ka ejang abon ba Maki, ebangenahb ebangenahb.  
\v 32 Adi elehkelkv nya a, nya Mosis bake no go edi ebale bal ji Moab, a lꞌsiiri aya ma Jodan ero bi Jeriko.  
\v 33 Wo Mosis kaam etꞌtohngo ji Levi edi ajehng ajehng, tibre Jehova, Esowo bi Isreel, ebnyam re ye wo bahke jolo ejum elehkelkv ebo. 
\c 14  
\s1 Mbake Nyi Edi Ndi Go Erede Bi Jodan 
\p  
\v 1 A wo li adi nya anebe Isreel ko no ana ejum elehkelkv ebo, go ndi nyi Kenan, nya Elieja nlimanjom, a Josua mmona Nun, a atubesi atˈtohngo Isreel bake ka anebe Isreel.  
\v 2 Bo tubu elfaange bake ndi nyio ka etˈtohngo ebsehmwubu kunu ejang, ana Jehova ka Mosis elkahn.  
\v 3 Mosis ebtohko ka etˈtohngo ebbal kunu ejang edi elehkelkv ebo go ero aya ma Jodan. Wo Mosis kaam anebe Levi edi elehkelkv ajehng ajehng semme atˈtohngo nyako.  
\v 4 Wo abon ba Josef ebjol etˈtohngo na ebbal, Manase abola Efriim. Abone Levi bo bakem ndi anyehng anyehng ka bo, bo ka bo agburu ajahbe nya nya re bo lene, a edi ndi enyam aleke.  
\v 5 Ano wo abone Isreel baange adi ndi ana Jehova ka Mosis elkahn. 
\s1 Hebron Bo Ka Keleb 
\p  
\v 6 Owo aneblum ba Juda kehm ba kpiri Josua ngare nyi á li go Gilgal, wo Keleb mmona Jefune ji lohng go Keniji, kehm tongo Josua re, Á kpˈkahne ji Jehova bungu tong Mosis nne Esowo nlokeltum ewe bada a wo a me go Kedes Bania.  
\v 7 Ngare nyio n jolo nnya atahl abal eji Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova tum-m go Kedes Benia re me n song feede edi ndi jio. N ko ji n nyehne no ba tong-e, ana ntir atahng enyame jolo no.  
\v 8 Wo abonanee ba e je ano bungu nsol nyi kake ane elfahle. Me, n toono Jehova a eltim eltim ename kpee.  
\v 9 Fvfo efung bio Mosis tir tong-m re, <<Ndi nyi akpade enya jene no bahke jolo ejum elehkelkv eja, a ji abon eba go njinanjini, tib eji a ma toono Jehova Esowo ebame a eltim eltim ena.  
\v 10 Anv ana Jehova ko nwongo, a ma-m bum go elkpin go nnya atahl abal a nnya elon nyia, bomo ngare nyi á bungu nsol nyia sehng go nnyo mi Mosis, ngare nyio nyi Isreel jo yannge go elka emahng ni ki kpi ajele. Nyehn me a lela, m ma kang nnya atahl ani, a nnya elon.  
\v 11 N kpeka li eko eko ana n jolo ngare nyi Mosis tum-m no, m bahke ma kpe je ebta anv ana n jo ngare nyio.  
\v 12 Anv, ka-m edi awong awong jia, ji ji Jehova ko nwongo efung bio. Wofono wˈwuk re anebe Anak lene o, ajahbe ebo jolo agburu ajahbe, bo si akahme sennge ejahbe ebo kak. Wo go ekakebo ji Jehova, m bahke kame bo yehke ana Jehova bungu no.  
\v 13 Owo Josua kehm fuulu Keleb mmona Jefune, fere ka-e Hebron ana ejum elehkelkv eje.  
\v 14 Fvfo bomo go ngare nyio Hebron li ka Keleb mmona Jefune, ye ji jolo nnea Keneji, tib eji á toono Jehova Esowo bi Isreel a eltim eltim ene.  
\v 15 Hebron bo jo lungu wuku wuku re Kiriat Arba, Arba wo lini ebehn mbing nyia, á jolo etahntahn nne no lohng go Anak. Owo ndi re ekv go nta anoko. 
\c 15  
\s1 Ejang ndi ji bo ka Juda 
\p  
\v 1 Bo tubu elfaange bak edi ndi ka etˈtohngo ji Juda ji a, ebangenahb ebangenahb, kpange rehng go Edom tete song rehng go elka emahng Jiin ni ki kpi ajele, feere go esˈkohlo ji ejang eboblum.  
\v 2 Nseenge nyi ejang eboblum, bomo go nkpe nyi ejang eboblum nyi Aya Akang,  
\v 3 sehnge eboblum eboblum bi mbang nyi li go eyake agburu awong Akrabim, song rehng go Jiin, tete song rehng go ejang eboblum bi Kedes-Bania. Tob sehnge go Hejiron rehng go Ada, gahl song rehng go Karka.  
\v 4 Ano wo sehnge no, song rehng go Ajimon, kehm song yel go ebgba bi Ijib, song fel go agburu ma a lˈkˈma nyehn egbuk jehko. Nseenge ebo nyi ejang eboblum nyi a.  
\v 5 Nseenge nyi ero nfam, jolo go aya akang ,tete song rehng go nnyo mi aya Jodan. Nseenge nyi ejang ebobkal bomo go nkpe aya akang nnyo aya Jodan,  
\v 6 sehng asongo ero ero Bet-Hogla, sehng ano ebobkal ebobkal bio bi Bet-Araba, song rehng go eltal ni Bohan ji mmon no nlum no Ruben.  
\v 7 Nseenge nyio bomo go edamme ji Ako, asongo go Debir, sehng ebobkal ebobkal asongo go Gilgal, nyi jolo songo songo go mbang nyi li eyake eyake agburu awong nyi bo kpo lung re Adumin. A wo sehnge rehng go ejang eboblum bi edamme, soro asi alahb ma En Semes, tete ba lohng ga En Rogel.  
\v 8 Tob sehnge go edamme ji Ben Hinom, feere go edamme ji ejang eboblum bi Jebus ji li Jeusalem. Sehnge asongo, wahr go ewong ji li go erede edamme ji Hinom, song rehng go ekahlsi, ejang ebobkal bi edamme ji Refayiim.  
\v 9 Nseenge nyio soro asi go ero ewong song rehng go mbˈbehl alahb ma Neftoa tete ba lohng ga ajahbe nya ewong Efron, feere song rehng go Baala, ji li Kiriat-Jearim.  
\v 10 Nseenge kehm kpe sehng erede erede bio bi Baala asongo go egburu ewong ji Seya, sehng nkpe ewong ejang ebobkal, bi Jearim, ji li Kesalon, , sehng asongo go Bet-Semes siiri rehng go Timna.  
\v 11 Nseenge nyio soro asi asongo go ejang ebobkal nyi Ekron, sennge asongo go Sikeron, song rehng egburu ewong Baala, song rehng Jabnel. Nseenge song fele agburu aya ma nne lˈkˈnyehn ma egbuk jehko.  
\v 12 Nseenge nyi jolo erede nfam, jolo nkpe agburu aya, ma nne lˈkˈma nyehn egbuk jehko. Nseenge nyi jolo sennge anebe Juda nyi a, go ebangenahb ebangenahb. 
\s1 Keleb Noko Ga Hebron a Debir Go Ebta 
\p  
\v 13 Ana Jehova Ka Josua elkahn re á ka Keleb ji mmona Jefune, edi ndi go Juda. Josua kehm kake Keleb ejahbe ji bo kpo lung re Kiriat-Aba ji li Hebron. Aba ji jolo nde no nkul no Anak.  
\v 14 Keleb wo kame anebe Anak yehke go Hebron, bo ane na ara, Sesayi, Ahiman, a Talmayi, bo kpee lohng go ebangenahb ji Anak.  
\v 15 Edi jio wo á mehle song nok a ane ba lene goDebir wuku wuku bo jo lungu edi jio re Kiriat- Sefer.  
\v 16 Keleb kehm bungu re, <<Nne awohng awohng no lˈnok a Kiriat Sefer fere ga bo, m bahk-e kake mmon ewame no nkal no bo kpo lung-e re Aksa go elbal.>>  
\v 17 Otꞌniel mmon no nlum no Kenaji, ji jolo mmonannyehna Keleb wo je song nok a bo fere ga bo. Keleb kehm-e kake Aksa mmon ewe go elbal.  
\v 18 Efung abehng eji Aksa ba goji Otˈniel, á kehm fanne Otˈniel re á bahb Keleb nde re á ka-e edi ndi. Ana Aksa kpꞌbadde go mbvankang, owo Keleb nde kehm-e bahbe re, <<Jenji a kpꞌsebe re me n lim ka-a?>>  
\v 19 Owo á kehm-e faange re, <<Lim ekahmekahme ejum ka-m. Nong me n fil-a ndon, eji a ma-m ka edi ndi ji li go ejang eboblum, tob ka-m mbꞌbehl alahb.>> Owo Keleb kehm-e kake abing alahb nya li go ewong, a edamme. 
\s1 Ajahbe Nya Bo Ka Juda 
\p  
\v 20 Edi ndi elehkelkv ji a ji bo bake ka etꞌtohngo Juda, go ebangenahb ebangenahb:  
\v 21 Ajahbe nyaa nya ga li go ejang eboblum,go etꞌtohngo ji Juda, go emahng ji ejang eboblum, feere go nkonandi nyi Edom: Kabjeel, Ada, Jagu,  
\v 22 Kina, Dimona, Adada,  
\v 23 Kedes, Hajo, Itꞌnan,  
\v 24 Jif, Telem, Bealod,  
\v 25 Hajo Hadata, Keriot Hejiron ji li Hajo,  
\v 26 Amam, Sema, Molada,  
\v 27 Haja Gada, Hesmon, Beti-Peleti,  
\v 28 Haja Sual, Beseba Bisiotiya,  
\v 29 Baala, Iyim, Ejem,  
\v 30 Eltolad, Kesil, Homa,  
\v 31 Jiklak, Madmana, Sansana,  
\v 32 Lebaoti, Silhim, Ayin, a Rimon, kpee jolo eltahl ejahbe ebsuwubu bi nnen, a abon ajahbe bako ba nse.  
\v 33 Ajahbe nyako nya jolo nnahb ewong nya jolo feere go erede, nya bo tob ka Juda: Estaol, Jora, Asna,  
\v 34 Janoa, En Ganim, Tapua, Enam,  
\v 35 Jamuti, Adulam, Soko, Ajeka,  
\v 36 Saarayim, a Aditayim, a Gedara ji ji tob li Gederotayim, jolo ewubu ejahbe ebni, a abon ajahbe ba nse.  
\v 37 Jenan, Hadasa, Mikdal Gad,  
\v 38 Dilen, Mijipa, Joktel,  
\v 39 Lakis, Bojikati, Eglon,  
\v 40 Kabon, Lamas, Kitlis,  
\v 41 Gederoti, Bet Dagon, Naama, Makeda, kpee jolo elku ejahbe ajehng, a abon ajahbe ba nse.  
\v 42 Libna, Eteri, Asan,  
\v 43 Ibta, Asna, Nejib,  
\v 44 Keila, Akijib, Maresa, ejahbe ebsehmwubu, a abon ajahbe ebo bako ba nse.  
\v 45 Ekron, a nsi nyi senng-e kak, a abon ajahbe ba nse.  
\v 46 Bomo go Erede bi Ekron, ajahbe kpee nya jolo sennge Asdod, a nsi nyi sennge kak, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 47 Asdod, a nsi nyi li senng-e kak, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse, Gaja, a nsi nyi senng-e kak, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse, bomo go abongba ba Ijib, tete rehng go abongba Ijib, nkpe nkpe agburu aya ma nne lꞌkꞌma nyehn egbuk ma li Mediterinian.  
\v 48 Fvfo go edi awong awong: Samir, Jatir, Soko,  
\v 49 Dana, Kiriati Sana ji li Debi,  
\v 50 Anab, Estemo, Anim,  
\v 51 Gosen, Holon, a Gilo, ewubu ejahbe ajehng, abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 52 Arab, Duma, Esan,  
\v 53 Janim, Bet-Tapua, Afeka,  
\v 54 Humta, Kiriat-Abaji li hebron a Jior, ejahbe ebsuwubu, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 55 Maon, Kamel, Jif, Juta,  
\v 56 Jejirel, Jokdim, Janoa,  
\v 57 Kain, Gibea, a Timna, jolo ejahbe ebwubu, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 58 Halhul, Beti Jur, Gedo,  
\v 59 Maarat, Beti Anoti, a Eltekon, ejahbe ebrakebra, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 60 Kiriati Baal ji li Kiriati Jearim, a Raba, ejahbe ebbal, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 61 Go emahng ji ajele kꞌlꞌmahng: Beti Araba, Midin, Sekaka,  
\v 62 Nibsan, ejahbe akang, a En Gedi, ejahbe ebrakebra, a abon ajahbe ebo bako ba nse.  
\v 63 Anebe Juda maam kam anebe Jebus yehke, bo ji lene go Jeusalem, tete sik anebe Jebus baa kpeka lene semme a anebe Juda tete sik lela. 
\c 16  
\s1 Edi Ndi Ji Bo Ka Efriim Abola Manase 
\p  
\v 1 Bo tumu elfaange bak edi ndi ka etˈtohngo ji Josef, edi elehkelkv ebo bomo go aya ma Jodan, ero bio bi ngba nyi Jeriko, sehng go elka emahng ji kꞌlꞌmahng ajele tete song rehng go edi awong awong ji Betel.  
\v 2 Sehng o Betel ji bo jo lung re Luji siiri song rehng go Ataroti ji li go elwo ni anebe Arki,  
\v 3 feere ejang erede erede bio bi anebe Jafleti, tete rehng go ejang erede bi Beti Horon, song rehng go Gejer, tete song fel go agburu aya ma nne lꞌkꞌma nyehn egbuk jehko ji li Mediterinian.  
\v 4 Ano wo Manase, a Efriim bo ji lohng go etˈtohngo ji Josef ko edi elehkelkv ebo.  
\v 5 Ana wo bo bake ndi nyia ka Efriim, bo bake ebangenahb ebangenahb: Nseenge edi elehkelkv ebo, bomo go Ataroti Ada jio ji li go ero bi Beti Horon,  
\v 6 sehng song yel agburu aya ma nne lꞌkꞌma nyehn egbuk jehko. Bomo go Mikmetad, ji li go ejang ebobkal, gahl feere go ero nfam asongo go Taanati Silo, nkpe nkpe song rehng go Janoa ji li go ero nfam.  
\v 7 Ano wo sehnge nkpe nkpe nyio nyi Janoa song rehng go Ataroti, a Naara, sehng song kooro Jeriko, fere ba lohng go aya ma Jodan.  
\v 8 Bomo go Tapua, nseenge feere erede erede, toono nrabbe ebgba bi Kana, fere song fel go agburu aya ma nne lꞌkꞌma nyehn egbuk jehko. Ana wo etˈtohngo ji Efriim ko ndi ebo ebangenahb ebangenahb.  
\v 9 Bo tob ka bo abon ajahbe ba nlen, a ba nse, nya bo bumu eje eje ka anebe Efriim go ellong nsol elehkelkv nyi anebe Manase.  
\v 10 Bo kamem anebe Kenan ba jolo go Geja; Tete tub lela anebe Kenan baa go lene ellong anebe Efriim, wo anebe Efriim kpo ko bo fubu eltum. 
\c 17  
\s1 Edi ndi Ji Bo Ka Go Erede 
\p  
\v 1 Bo tubu elfaange bak edi ndi ka ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase. Manase ana ngbokambang a mmon no Josef. Makiri wo ko ejum elehkelkv, ye ji jolo ngbokambang a mmon no Manase. Makiri wo li nde no anebe Giled. Yeb tohko ko Giled, a Basan, tibre anebe Makiri jolo atahntahn abanokebta.  
\v 2 Mbake nyia joko ka erik ane bako go ellong anebe Manase, go abangenahb nyaa, Abieja, Helek, Asriel, Sekem, Hefa, a Semida. A wo li erik aneblum bako etˈtohngo ji Manase mmona Josef, go ebo ebangenahb.  
\v 3 Ana jolo o, Selofehad mmon no Hefa, ye ji Giled jel-e no, Giled ji jolo mmon no Makiri, ye ji Manase jel-e no, jelem mmon awohng awohng no nlum. Á jele abon ba nkal ba ba . Abing ebo nya a, Mala, Noa, Hogla, Milka, a Tisa.  
\v 4 Abon ba nkal baa kehm mehle song kpiri Elieja nlimanjom, a Josua mmona Nun, a atubesi ejahbe ba Isreel, kehm bungu re, <<Jehova ka Mosis elkahn re, á ka-r mbaka ndi nyˈnyahre ana bo ka abonanyehn ba nlum go egahre ellong. Josua kehm kake bo ejum elehkelkv semme a ellong abonanyehn nde ebo, jang jang ana Jehova bo elkahn.  
\v 5 Manase bo bake ka-e erohko ndi na ewubu, kehm budu ejang bi Giled, a bi Basan, ji li ero bi aya ma Jodan,  
\v 6 tibre abon ba nkal go etˈtohngo ji Manase ko mbake ana abon ba nlum. Edi ndi ji Giled, li ka erik etˈtohngo ji Manase.  
\v 7 Edi ndi ji Manase bomo go Aser, rehng go Mikmetati go ero bi Sekem. Nseenge nyio feere eboblum eboblum bio bi Mikmetati sehng goji ane ba lene kohlo elbing alahb ni En Tapua.  
\v 8 Ndi nyi Tapua li ka Manase, yefono Tapua li go nseenge nyi Manase, li ka anebe Efriim.  
\v 9 Nseenge sehnge asongo eboblum eboblum, song rehng go nrabbe ebgba bi Kana. Ajahbe jˈjol nya jolo ka anebe Efriim nya li nkpe nkpe nyi ajahbe nya Manase, wo nseenge nyi Manase jolo go nkpe nyi ejang ebobkal bi nrabbe ebgba tete song rehng agburu aya ma nne lˈkˈ ma nyehn egbuk jehko.  
\v 10 Ejang eboblum ndi nyio jolo ka aneb Efriim, go ejang ebobkal jol ka anebe Manase. Ndi nyi Manase kpange rehng go aya ma nne lˈkˈma nyehn egbuk jehko, á kpi nseenge a Aser go ejang ebobkal, go ero nfam nseenge rehnge go Isaka.  
\v 11 Atahng ajahbe nya Isaka, a Aser, Manase tob kpi Beti-San, Ibleyam, a anebe Dor ji li anebe Dor, Endo, Taanak, Megido, a nsi nyi li sennge kak. (Etoono ebra jolo Nafod)  
\v 12 Jol tvtv o, etˈtohngo ji Manase maam lene abon ajahbe bao kpee. Tib anebe Kenan bumu ntir abo re bo tiki lene erohko ndi jio.  
\v 13 Wo eji anebe Isreel gbale go atahne. Bo rodo anebe Kenan bum aju, bo jo loko bo. Bo kamem bo kpee yehke go ebo ejang ejahbe.  
\v 14 Owo etˈtohngo ji Josef kehm ba kpiri Josua, kehm-e bahbe re, <<Jenji wahnge a bahk-r kake edi ndi ajehng ji ji ana edi elehkelkv? Wahr ebjol go nrur, Jehova ma-r fuulu gbˈgbal.  
\v 15 Josua kehm faange re, <<Lˈjol re wahn ebrur sehng, lˈfere jol re edi ndi ji edi awong awong ji Efriim gbalem ka-n, song-n go ekulugbe wahn song ja edi ndi ka enahne, go edi ji anebe Peres, a anebe Refa.>>  
\v 16 Anebe Josef kehm bungu re, <<Edi awong awong wahr gbalem, ga anebe Kena ba li go ebal kpi amvtv akuungu, bo ji lene go Beti San, a nsi ebo, a bo ji li go edamme ji Jejireel.  
\v 17 Wo, Josua kehm tongo etˈtohngo ji Josef, ji li Efriim a Manase, <<Wahn ebrur, fere tˈtahne, ń nehm bel edi ndi ajehng ji ji,  
\v 18 bo bahke tob ka-n ekulugbe jio ji edi awong awong. Ja-n ana bahk-n gbale, jol jˈjahne; Jol afi anebe Kenan bele amvtv akuungu, afi bo bele atahne, ḿ bahke ma kam bo yehke.>> 
\c 18  
\s1 Ana Bo Bake Edi Ndi Ji Sa No 
\p  
\v 1 Anebe Isreel kpee kehm ba kono edi ajehng go Silo, kehm sehke Ebkpatahk Elwane, ngare nyia Isreel ebko ndi nyio kpee.  
\v 2 wo ngare nyia ebsa etˈtohngo na ebsehma bi bo kala ka bo edi ndi ji elehkeltv ebo.  
\v 3 Josua kehm tong anebe Isreel re, <<Bahke kange renan, ji ń kpꞌsiki, kehm mehle song ko adi ndi nya Jehova, Esowo bi babnso ejahne ka-n no?>>  
\v 4 Yehken ane ara ara, go etꞌtohngo ajehng ajehng. M bahke tumu bo re, bo song feede edi ndi jia fere nyon bade ana bo bahke bake ejum elehkelkv ka etꞌtohngo etꞌtohngo. Bo bahke feere ba tong-m.  
\v 5 Bo bahke bake edi ndi jio edi na ebsehma. Anebe Juda bahke sake go ebo a ndi, ejang eboblum, a anebe Josef go ebo a ndi, ejang ebobkal.  
\v 6 Eji ḿ ma nyon bade ana edi ndi ebsehma bio li no, ko-n ba ka-m, me n tub elfaange ka-n go esamahr bi Jehova Esowo ebahre.  
\v 7 Anebe Levi belem edi elehkelkv ajehng ajehng semme anahne, tibre eltum ni njom alimi ni li ejum elehkelkv ebo, ni bo kpo lim ka Jehova. Etꞌtohngo ji Gad, a ji Ruben, a ejang etꞌtohngo ji Manase, bob ko mbake ebo go ero nfam , ejang bio bi Jodan. Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova, wo ka bo.  
\v 8 Ana ane baa mehle asongo re bo song nyehn edi ndi, Josua tubu bo elle re, <<Songen, wahn song nyehn edi ndi, fere nyon ana edi ndi jio li no. Ko-n ba kam, m bahke tubu elfaange ka-n a Silo, go esamahr bi Jehova.>>  
\v 9 Ano wo aneblum bao mehle no yannge kpee go ndi nyio, fere nyon ana bo nyehne no ejahbe ejahbe kak go nwer. Bo bake ndi nyio go edi na ebsehma, feere ba kpiri Josua go edi erekekv go Silo.  
\v 10 Josua kehm tubu elfaange ka bo go esamahr Jehova go Silo, kehm bake anebe Isreel edi ndi jio ana bo li no, etꞌtohngo etꞌtohngo. 
\s1 Edi Ndi Ji Bo Ka Benjamin 
\p  
\v 11 Ngbokambang elfaange gbo tub etꞌtohngo ji Benjamin, ebangenahb ebangenahb. Edi elehkelkv ebo li go elka elka ni etꞌtohngo ji Juda abola Josef:  
\v 12 Nseenge nyi jolo ejang ebobkal, bomo go aya ma Jodan, sehng ano go ejang ebobkal bi Jeriko, sehng feere erede asongo go edi awong awong, tete ba lohng go elka emahng ni kꞌlꞌmahng ajele ni Beti Aven.  
\v 13 Siiri o song rehng go ejang eboblum, asongo go Lujiji li Betel, sehng asongo go Ataroti Ada ji kun go ewong, ejang eboblum bi Beti Horon ji rede rede.  
\v 14 Nseenge sehnge ejang eboblum go erede, bomo ewong ji li mbuksong nyi Beti Horon, tete song kohlo go ejahbe ji bo kpo lung re Kariati Baal(ji li Kariat Jearim, ejahbe jia wob go ellong ajahbe nya li ka Juda. A wo li erede nfam .  
\v 15 Nseenge nyi ejang eboblum bomo go esi ejahbe ji Kariati-Jearim, sehnge ano erede nfam, erede nfam, tete ba lohng go mbꞌbehl alahb nyi Neftoa.  
\v 16 Nseenge sehnge asongo nkpe ewong nkpe ewong nyi li wane edamme jio ji Ben Hinom, ejang ebobkal bi edamme ji Refiam. Ano wo sehnge go edamme ji Hinom, mbang nyi fi nkpale nkpale go ejahbe ji anebe Jebus, tete rehng go En-Rogel.  
\v 17 Fere gahl feere ebobkal asongo go En-Semes, tete rehng go Gelilod ji li songo songo mbang awong nyi Adumim, song rehng go eltal ni Bohan ji mmon no nlum no Ruben.  
\v 18 Sehnge o asongo nkpe nkpe egburu ewong ji Beti Araba, tete song rehng Araba.  
\v 19 Tob sehnge asongo ejang ebobkal, nkpe nkpe egburu ewong ji Beti Hogla, tete ba lohng go efabe agburu aya akang ma a lˈkˈma nyehn egbuk jehko, ma ba wane go nnyo aya ma Jodan. Nseenge nyi ejang eboblum nyi a.  
\v 20 Aya ma Jodan ma jolo nseenge go ero nfam. Adi ndi nya a, nya tibi nseenge nyi ejum elehkelkv ji abangenahb nya Benjamin ajang kpe kpe.  
\v 21 Agburu ajahbe nya a, nya bo ka etꞌtohngo ji Benjamin: Jeriko, Beti Hogla, Emek-Kejii,  
\v 22 Beti Araba, Jemarayim, Betel,  
\v 23 Avim, Para, Ofra,  
\v 24 Kefa Amoni, Ofni, a Geba, kpee jol egburu ejahbe ewubu ejahbe ebbal a abon ajahbe ba nse.  
\v 25 Gibion, Rama, Beeroti,  
\v 26 Mijipa, Kefira, Moja,  
\v 27 Rekem, Ipiil, Tarala,  
\v 28 Jela, Haelef, a ejahbe anebe Jebus ji li Jeusalem, Gibea, a Kiriati, jolo ewubu ejahbe ebni, a abon ajahbe ba nse. Nyaa nya jolo ejum elehkelkv ji etꞌtohngo ji Benjamin a ebangenahb ebangenahb. 
\c 19  
\s1 Edi ndi ji Bo Ka Etˈtohngo Ji Simion 
\p  
\v 1 Etoono elfaange ni bo tubu no gbo tub etˈtohngo ji Simion, ebangenahb ebangenahb. Edi elehkelkv ebo woomo ejang ejahbe ji etˈtohngo ji Juda.  
\v 2 Ajahbe nya a, nya wob go atahng: Beeseba a Seba, Molada,  
\v 3 Haja-Sual, Bala, Ejem,  
\v 4 Eltolad, Betul, Homa,  
\v 5 Jiklag, Beti-Makaboti, Haja-Susa,  
\v 6 Beti-Lebaoti, a Saruhen, kpee jolo ewubu ejahbe ebra, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 7 Ain, Rimon, Ede, a Asan, egburu ejahbe ebni, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse,  
\v 8 ajahbe kpee nya li sennge agburu ajahbe song rehng go Baalati Beer ji li Rama go elka emahng ni kˈlˈ mahng ajele. A wo jolo edi elehkelkv ji etˈtohngo ji Simion, ebangenahb ebangenahb.  
\v 9 Edi elehkelkv ji li ka etˈtohngo ji Simion lohng go edi elehkelkv ji etˈtohngo ji Juda, tibre edi ndi ji bo ka etˈtohngo ji Juda gbale sehng ana bo jol-e kake. Ano wo anebe Simion ko edi elehkelkv ebo go atahng edi elehkelkv ji etˈtohngo ji Juda. 
\s1 Edi ndi ji Bo Ka Etˈtohngo Ji Jebulon 
\p  
\v 10 Go elfaange ebra nyi bo tubu no, gbo tub etˈtohngo ji Jebulon, ebangenahb ebangenahb. Nseenge edi elehkelkv ebo jolo tete rehng Sarid.  
\v 11 Sehng o jo tahm erede erede, song rehng go Marala, sehng kooro Dabeseti, ano wo sehnge song rehng abongba ba li kohlo Jokneam.  
\v 12 Ano wo sehnge asongo go Sarid, ero nfam, ero nfam, ji njul kpo lohng, tete song rehng nseenge nyi Kisloti Tabor, sehnge asongo go Daberati tete rehng go Jafia.  
\v 13 Owo soro asi ano, ero nfam, ero nfam, rehng Gati-hefa, a Eti Kajin, ba lohng ga Rimon, song gahl asongo go Nea.  
\v 14 Nseenge nyi ejang ebobkal sehnge Hanaton tete song rehng go edamme ji Ipta El.  
\v 15 Ajahbe nya jolo o nya a, Kata, Nahalal, Simron, Idala, a Betlehem, agburu ajahbe jolo ewubu ejahbe ebbal, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 16 Ajahbe, a abon ajahbe ba edi elehkelkv nya bo bake ka Jebulon nya a, ebangenahb ebangenahb. 
\s1 Edi Ndi Ji Bo ka Etˈtohngo Ji Isaka 
\p  
\v 17 Go elfaange eni nyi bo tubu no gbo tub etˈtohngo ji Isaka, ebangenahb ebangenahb.  
\v 18 Nseenge ebo nyi sehnge go Jejireel, Kesuloti, Sunem,  
\v 19 Hafarayim, Sion, Anaharati,  
\v 20 Rabiti, Kision, Ebeji,  
\v 21 Remeti, En-ganim, En-hada, Beti-Pajiji,  
\v 22 Nseenge ebo kooro Tabo, Sahajuma, Beti-Semes, sehnge ano tete song kohlo go aya ma Jodan, jolo elku egburu ejahbe ajehng, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 23 Agburu ajahbe nyaa, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse, nya nya jolo edi elehkelkv ji etˈtohngo ji Isaka, ebangenahb ebangenahb. 
\s1 Edi ndi Ji Bo Ka Etˈtohngo ji Aser 
\p  
\v 24 Go elfaange na elon, nyi bo tubu no gbo tub etˈtohngo ji Aser, ebangenahb ebangenahb.  
\v 25 Ajahbe nyaa nya tob woomo go atahng: Helkati Hali, Beten, Aksaf,  
\v 26 Alammelek, Amad, a Misal. Nseenge nyi jolo go erede nfam sehnge go Kamel song rehng go Siho-libnati.  
\v 27 Tob sennge asongo ero bi Beti-Dagon, tob kooro Jebulon, Edamme ji Ipta El, fere feere ejang ebobkal asongo go Beti-Emek, a Neiel, ano wo yabe Kabul tv ejang ebobkal.  
\v 28 Sehnge song rehng go Abdon, Rehob, Hamon, a Kana tete song rehng go Sidon ji kpˈgake gbal.  
\v 29 Nseenge nyio fere sehnge asongo go Rama, sehng asongo go Taya ji si ekahme sennge elbo kak, ba rehng go Hosa, fere sehng song lohng aya ma nne lˈkˈ nyehn egbuk jehko, go ejang ndi nyi Akjib,  
\v 30 Uma, Afek, a Rehob. Jolo eltahl egburu ejahbe ebbal, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse.  
\v 31 Agburu ajahbe nyaa, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse, nya nya jolo edi elehkelkv ji etˈtohngo ji Aser ebangenahb ebangenahb. 
\s1 Edi ndi ji Bo ka Etˈtohngo Ji Naftali 
\p  
\v 32 Go elfaange erakera ni bo tubu no, gbo tub etˈtohngo ji Naftali, ebangenahb ebangenahb:  
\v 33 Nseenge ebo bomo go Helef a egburu eti ji Jaananim, sehng asongo go Adami Nekeb, a Jabnel rehng go Lakum, song fel go aya ma Jodan.  
\v 34 Nseenge sehnge feere erede, sehng go Ajinoti Tabor tete ba lohng go Hukok. Nseenge kooro Jebulon go ejang eboblum, go erede kooro Aser, a Aya ma Jodan go ero nfam.  
\v 35 Ajahbe nya bo si akahme sennge kak nya a, Jidehm, Jer, Hamati, Rakati, Kinereti,  
\v 36 Adama, Rama, Hajo,  
\v 37 Kedes, Edrei, En Hao,  
\v 38 Iron, Mikdal El, Horem, Beti-Anati, Beti Semes, jolo elku egburu ejahbe ebni, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse .  
\v 39 Agburu ajahbe nyaa, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse, nya nya jolo edi elehkelkv ji etˈtohngo ji Naftali, ebangenahb ebangehb. 
\s1 Edi ndi Ji Bo Ka Etˈtohngo Ji Dan 
\p  
\v 40 Go elfaange esehma nyi bo tubu no gbo tub etˈtohngo ji Dan, ebangenahb ebangenahb.  
\v 41 Nseenge nyi edi elehkelkv rehng: Jora, Estaol, Ir Semes,  
\v 42 Saalabin, Aijalon, Itla,  
\v 43 Elon, Timna, Ekron,  
\v 44 Elteke, Gibeton, Baalati,  
\v 45 Jehud, Bene Berak, a Gati Rimon,  
\v 46 Me Jakon, a Rakon, a edi ji li go mbuksong nyi Jopa.  
\v 47 Riidi etˈtohngo ji Dan sehng re bo kehm koko edi ebo go ebo ane ba tohko jol o. Bo mehle song nok a Lesem, wul nne awohng awohng o, fere ko ndi bo fere jol o. Bo lene go Lesem, feere yaange mbing ejahbe nyio, jo lung re Dan, mbing nyi nde ebo no nkul.  
\v 48 Agburu ajahbe nyaa, a abon ajahbe ebo ba nse, nya nya jolo edi elehkelkv ji etˈtohngo ji Dan, ebangenahb ebangenahb. 
\s1 Edi Ndi Ji Bo Ka Josua 
\p  
\v 49 Eji bo ma baange ndi nyia kpee mal, arohko arohko, anebe Isreel kehm kimi edi tob ka Josua mmona Nun, edi elehkelkv á tob jol o a bo,  
\v 50 ana Jehova ka bo elkahn. Ajahbe nya á bahbe re bo ka-e nya nya bo ka-e no, ana Timnati Sera ji li go edi awong awong ji Efriim. Josua si ejahbe jio fere lene o.  
\v 51 Adi ndi nya a, nya Elieja nlimanjom, a Josua mmona Nun, a atubesi ba abangenahb ba atˈtohngo nya anebe Isreel, bake go elfaange ni bo tubu go Silo, go esamahr Jehova. Bo yiimi go mbuga mi Ebkpatahk Elwane. Ano wo mbake nyi adi ndi nyaa kohlo no. 
\c 20  
\s1 Ajahbe Nya Elbeke Biiri 
\p  
\v 1 Owo Jehova kehm bungu tong Josua re,  
\v 2 <<Tong anebe Isreel bo yehke ajahbe elbeke biiri, ana m bungu tong-n sehng go nnyo mi Mosis,  
\v 3 ngare anyehng anyehng nyi nne lˈwul nne go efin, eji á ki-e wul elrang, á bahke beke song yel o, eji akunu nya nkvne lˈki-e ba wul, bongo go alung ma ma fad.  
\v 4 Á lꞌbe asongo go ekahmekahme ajahbe nyao , á bahke sake yiimi go eti mbu ji ejahbe jio, tooro ajehng ajehng ana jolo no tong anebkul nfam ba ejahbe jio. Owo bo bahk-e koko ka-e edi re á jol a bo ejahbe bo.  
\v 5 Ababꞌbongo ba kpˈsebe re bo bongo go alung ma ma fad, kpe-e kame lꞌba, anebkul ejahbe kꞌtiki yehke nne noo ka, tibre nne noo wulem nne ebjing ewe go elrang, afi go ebi ntir.  
\v 6 Nne noo bahke sake ejahbe jio tete bo lam elam eje gbul gbul gbuul, fvfo tete ngare nyi Ntubesi nlimanjom no jolo no ngare nyi efin bio limi no kpo. Owo á bahke feere kehnge go ege etahk, go ege ejahbe ji a be no.  
\v 7 Bo yehke Kedes ji li go Galili, edi awong awong ji Naftali, a Sekem edi ndi ji Efriim ji jolo awong awong, a Kariati-Abaji li Hebron li go edi awong awong ji Juda.  
\v 8 Go ero bi aya ma Jodan kohlo Jeriko, bo yehke Bejar ji li go elka emahng ni ki kpi ajele, go ero ewong ji li ebal ebal, go etꞌtohngo ji Ruben, bo tob yehke Ramoti ji li go Giled ji etꞌtohngo ji Gad, a Golan ji li go Basan, ji li go etꞌtohngo ji Manase.  
\v 9 Nne Isreel awohng awohng, afi jolo njenne, nyi lene a bo, lꞌwul nne go efin bahke ma be, song yel go ajahbe nya bo ma yehke, abꞌbongo ba bahke sebe re bo bongo alung mao, bo kehm lame elam eje gbul gbul gbuul, nehm ma lim ano. 
\c 21  
\s1 Ajahbe Nya Bo Ka etˈtohngo Ji Levi 
\p  
\v 1 Atubesi ba anebe Levi kehm ba kpiri Elieja nlimanjom, a Josua ji mmona Nun, a atubesi bako ba atˈtohngo nyako nya Isreel  
\v 2 kehm ba tong bo go Silo go Kenan re, <<Jehova bungu sehng go nnyo mi Mosis re, wahn ka-r agburu ajahbe wahr lene, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke.  
\v 3 Owo anebe Isreel kehm kake anebe Levi ajahbe nyao, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, go ebo ejum elehkelkv ana Jehova ka elkahn:  
\v 4 Ngbokambanga elfaange ni bo tubu no gbo tub anebe Kohad, ebangenahb ebangnahb. Anebe Levi, bo ji lohng ebangenahb ji Eron nlimanjom, bo ka bo ewubu egburu ejahbe ebra. Ajahbe nyaa kpee lohng go atˈtohngo nyaa; Juda, Simion, a Benjamin.  
\v 5 Erik etˈtohngo ji anebe Kohati, bo ka bo agburu ajahbe na ebwubu, nya lohng go atˈtohngo nya Efriim, Dan, go ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase.  
\v 6 Ebangenahb ji Gosen bo ka bo ewubu egburu ejahbe ebra, nya jolo go etˈtohngo ji Isaka, Asa, Naftali, a ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase ji li go Basan.  
\v 7 Go ebangenahb ji Merari, go ebangenahb ebangenahb, bo ko ewubu egburu ejahbe ebbal, nya lohng go etˈtohngo ji Ruben, Gad, a Jebulon.  
\v 8 Ana wo anebe Isreel ka anebe Levi ajahbe nyaa, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, ana Jehova ka Mosis elkahn.  
\v 9 Go etˈtohngo ji Juda, a Simion, bo bake agburu ajahbe nyao, go mbing a mbing.  
\v 10 Ajahbe nyaa bo bake ka ebangenahb ji Eron, bo ji lohng go ebangenahb ji Kohati, ji lohng go ebangenahb ji Levi. Tibre bo ba ngbokambang elfaange ni bo tubu no, gbo tub bo.  
\v 11 Bo ka bo Kiriati-Arba ji li Hebron. A edi ndi ji enyam aleke, ji li sennge bo kak, li go edi awong awong ji Juda. (Aba wo jolo ndea nde no nkul no Anak).  
\v 12 Wo adi ndi, a abon ajahbe ba li sennge ejahbe jia bob tohko ka Keleb ji mmona Jefune, ana edi elehkelkv eje.  
\v 13 Go ebangenahb ji Eron nlimanjom, bo ka Hebron ejahbe ji nne no bo tongo re yeb wul nne, á bahke bake song biiri). Bo tob ka bo Libna,  
\v 14 Jati, Estemoa,  
\v 15 Holon, Debir,  
\v 16 Ain, Juta, a Beti Semes, semme edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo egburu ejahbe ebsuwubu bi lohng etˈtohngo jia na ebbal.  
\v 17 Go etˈtohngo ji Benjamin, bo ka bo Gibion, Geba,  
\v 18 Anatoti, a Almon, semme edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo egburu ejahbe ebni.  
\v 19 Nfange ajahbe nyi, jolo ka abalimajom, bo ji lohng go ebangenahb ji Eron, jolo ewubu ejahbe ebra, semme edi ndi ji enyam aleke.  
\v 20 Erik ebangenahb ji Kohati ji lohng go etˈtohngo ji Levi, bo ka bo ajahbe nyaa, nya lohng go etˈtohngo ji Efriim:  
\v 21 Go edi awong awong ji Efriim, bo ka bo Sekem, ejahbe ji nne lˈwul nne, á bahke bake biiri bo tob ka bo Gejar,  
\v 22 Kibjayim, Beti Horon, semme edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo egburu ejahbe ebni.  
\v 23 Fvfo go etˈtohngo ji Dan bo ka bo Elteke, Gebeton,  
\v 24 Aijalon, Gati rimon, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo egburu ejahbe ebni.  
\v 25 Go ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase, bo ka bo Taanak, Gati Rimon, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo egburu ejahbe ebbal.  
\v 26 Ejahbe ebwubu bio kpee, a edi ndi enyam aleke, bo ka erik ebangenahb ji Kohati.  
\v 27 Ajahbe nya a nya bo ka ebangenahb ji Gerson go etˈtohngo ji Levi: go ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase, bo ka bo Golan ji li go Basan, ejahbe ji nne lˈwul nne, á bahke bake biiri. Bo tob ka bo Estara, semme a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo ejahbe ebbal;  
\v 28 go etˈtohngo ji Isaka, bo ka bo Kision, a Daberati,  
\v 29 Jamuti, Ganim, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo ejahbe ebni.  
\v 30 Go etˈtonhgo ji Aser, bo ka bo Misal, Abdon,  
\v 31 Helkati, Rehob, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo egburu ejahbe ebni,  
\v 32 go etˈtohngo ji Naftali, bo ka bo Kedes ji li go Galili, ejahbe ji nne lˈwul nne, á bahke bake biiri. Bo tob ka bo Hamoti Dor, a Katan, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo ejahbe ebra.  
\v 33 Ajahbe nya bo ka anebe Gerson kpee jolo ewubu ejahbe ebra, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke.  
\v 34 A wo li ajahbe nya bo ka ebangenahb ji Merari, erik ebangenahb ji Levi: Go etˈtohngo ji Jebulon bo ka bo Jokneam, Karta,  
\v 35 Dimna, a Nahalal, budu edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo ejahbe ebni;  
\v 36 go etˈtohngo ji Ruben, bo ka bo Bejer, a Jahaji,  
\v 37 Kedemoti, a Mefaati, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo ejahbe ebni.  
\v 38 Go etˈtohngo ji Gad, bo ka bo Ramoti ji li go Giled, ejahbe ji nne lˈwul nne, á bahke bake biiri, bo tob ka Mahaneam,  
\v 39 Hesbon, Jajer, a edi ndi ji enyam aleke, jolo ejahbe ebni kpee.  
\v 40 Ajahbe kpee nya bo ka ebangenahb ji Merari, bo ji jolo erik anebe Levi jolo ewubu ejahbe ebbal.  
\v 41 Ajahbe nya anebe Isreel ka anebe Levi nya jolo go elwo ni Isreel jolo ejahbe atahl abal ejahbe ebnehkemni kpee , a edi ndi ji enyam aleke.  
\v 42 Ejahbe ajehng ajehng jio bele edi ndi ji enyam aleke semme kak. Jolo ano go etingitingi ajahbe nyaa kpee.  
\v 43 Ana wo Jehova ka anebe Isreel edi ndi jia kpee ana á nyame tong babnde ba nkul re á bahke kake bo. Ano wo bo ko ndi nyio kpee fere lene o.  
\v 44 Owo Jehova kehm kake bo erekekv go ejang abehng abehng, jang jang ana á nyame tong babnde ebo. Nnekv ebo awohng awohng limm no male yiimi a bo, tibre Jehova yake bo kpee kak go ebo abo.  
\v 45 Nnoobo enyam abehng abehng bi Jehova limm, bi á nyame tong Isreel bi kane no, kpee lˈlim. 
\c 22  
\s1 Atˈtohngo Nya Ero Nfam Feere Kehnge 
\p  
\v 1 Owo Josua kehm lungu etˈtohngo ji Ruben, a etˈtohngo ji Gad, a ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase re bo ba kono edi ajehng,  
\v 2 kehm bungu tong bo re,“Wahn eblim nsol kpee nyi Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova ka-n elkahn, wo go ejum ajehng ajehng ḿ me-e faabem nnyo ana n ka-n elkahn.  
\v 3 Bomo go njahm tete ba rehng efung bia, ń tikem be abonane ebahne sa, wahn ebtoono alum nya Jehova, Esowo ebahne ka-n no.  
\v 4 Anv Jehova, Esowo ebahne, ebka abonane ebahne erekekv ana á nyame no, feeren, kehnge go egahna ajahbe, go ndi nyi Mosis nlokeltuma Jehova ka-n no go egbuk aya jehko ji Jodan.  
\v 5 Wo belen ekunukpu, wahn bum ajehke a atahm nya Mosis nloketuma Jehova ka-n no, á tong-n re Jehova Esowo ebahne jo kor-n, wahn fere jo jen go mbang enye anyehng anyehng, tob jo bum atahm enye. Jabben ye tˈtahne, wahn fere jo lok-e a ntim a ntim enyahne kpee, a atohko atohko enyahne kpee.  
\v 6 Owo Josua kehm fuulu bo , fere tong bo re bo song. Bo kehm tahme go ebo ajahbe.  
\v 7 Mosis wo ka ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase edi go Basan, Josua ka erik etˈtohngo jia edi go erede nfam bi Jodan a abonanyehn ebo. Ana Josua tumu bo re bo song, á fuulu bo,  
\v 8 kehm fere bung re, <<Feeren kehnge go egahna ajahbe, a agburu afang enyahne, atohkondi enyahne, asilva, agul, abrons a akuungu, agburu nkohl abomo nya li tolok tolok. Song baange nsol nyia a abonane ebahne, nyi ḿ ma da goji anebekv ebahne.>>  
\v 9 Owo etˈtohngo Ruben, Gad, a ejang etꞌtohngo ji Manase kehm yake erik anebe Isreel o Silo ji li go Kenan, kehm jo feere go Giled ji li edi ndi ebo, ji bo ka bo, ana Jehova ka bo elkahn sehng go nnyo mi Mosis. 
\s1 Atꞌtohngo Nya Ero Nfam Limi Egudu Njom 
\p  
\v 10 Eji etˈtohngo ji Ruben, a ji Gad, a ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase ba rehng go Geliloti kohlo Jodan, go ndi nyi Kenan, bo kehm limi egburu egudu njom go nkpe aya Jodan.  
\v 11 Eji anebe Isreel wuku re boblim egudu njom go nkonkon nyi Kenan go Geliloti, kohlo Jodan, ejang bi Isreel  
\v 12 Isreel kpee kehm mehle song kono go Silo, re bo song nok ebta a bo.  
\v 13 Anebe Isreel kehm tumu Finehas ji mmon no nlum no Elieja nlimanjom, tv go ndi nyi Giled, re á song kpiri anebe Ruben, anebe Gad, a ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase.  
\v 14 Ane ba toon-e no jolo atubesi ane na awubu, no nne go etˈtohngo jˈje go Isreel, fvfo no nne jolo ntubesi go ege ebangenahb go ellong abangenahb nya anebe Isreel.  
\v 15 Eji bo je go Giled, goji anebe Ruben, anebe Gad, a ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase, bo kehm tongo bo re:  
\v 16 <<Ane kpee ba Jehova kpˈbungu re: <Nˈnan ḿ ma yab elnahne a Esowo bi Isreel mbang ana nyia? Nꞌnan wahnge ḿ ma sennge Jehova njahm, fere lim egudu njom ka elnahne anv, fere kpe-e tibi etahnsi?  
\v 17 Anv, abˈbi nya e limi go Peor wahr gbalema? Jol e ka tiki ru elnahre tete tub lela go abiafem nyao, jol eji li li re erem bia gbo tub ane ba Jehova!  
\v 18 << <Ń yahke sennge na Jehova njahma? Ń lˈtib etahnsi a Jehova lela, behna erakatahng eje bahke gboko tub anebe Isreel kpee.  
\v 19 Lˈjol re abˈbi ebjol go edi ndi ji ń ko no, feeren ba ga edi ndi ji Jehova, edi ji etahk ji Jehova li no, wahn ba baange ndi anahre. Kana nok a Jehova, afi a nahre re wahn song lim egudu njom ka elnahne, kˈsehnge egudu njom ji Jehova Esowo ebahre.  
\v 20 Eji Ekan, mmon no Jera da nsol nyi Esowo tongo re bo rannge, ń nyˈnehm ana erakatahng gbo tub Isreel kpeea? Ye ntahngtahng sang kpo no tib abiafem enye.> >>  
\v 21 Owo anebe Ruben, anebe Gad, go ejang etˈtohngo ji Manase kehm faange atubesi abangenahb nya Isreel re:  
\v 22 <<Nne no kpi Nsahm, Esowo, Jehova! Nne no kpi nsahm, Esowo Jehova. Á kpˈkahne! Nong Isreel kahn! Lˈfere jol re wahr ebten Esowo, fere senng-e njahm, kana wahr yake lela.  
\v 23 Lˈjol re e limi egudu njom ka elnahre re wahr yake Jehova, jo lim njom nyi eljahme fi, a nyi amohk nti. Afi fere lim ajom nya elkoono, nong yefono Jehova lim-r ji kor-e no.  
\v 24 Eˈee! E limi jia, a elfahle re behnjehle go abon ebahne bahke bungu tong ba bahre re, <Ejum ellimi ajii ń kpi a Jehova Esowo bi Isreel?  
\v 25 Jehova eblim aya Jodan re jol nseenge enyahre a wahn, wahn anebe Ruben, wahn anebe Gad! Ebo bahne wobem goji Jehova.> Wahngka etˈtohngo ejahne, bahke limi etˈtohngo ejahre re bo kˈkpe fahl Jehova .  
\v 26 Ejum jia ji wahnge e bungu re, ‘Wahr tooben lim egudu njom, wo nehm jol ka njom nyi bo kpo jahm fi, afi ajom nyako.  
\v 27 Tohko fere jol ano, bahke fere jol ejum ntianse ka wahr, a wahn, a aying nya kpˈbake njahm re, e bahke kake Jehova go ege etahk go ajom enyahre nya eljahme fi, a ajom nyako, a nya elkoono. Owo go esˈsong etˈtohngo ejahne nehm ma bung tong etˈtohngo ejahre re, Bo kpimm ebo abehng abehng goji Jehova.  
\v 28 Wo e bungu re, bo lˈfere bung jia tong-r, afi fere tong etˈtohngo ejahre, e bahke faange re, <Seengen, wahn nyehn elfoongo egudu njom ji Jehova ji babnsoo ejahre limi no, bo limem tib esi njom nyi eljahme fi, a ajom nyako, bo limi re jol ejum ntianse ka-r njahm ebal ebal.>  
\v 29 Ndan gbaa re wahr nok a Jehova, fere senng-e njahm lela, fere ba lim egudu jia re wahr jo lim ajom nya bo kpo jahm fi, a nya amohk nti, a ajom nyako, sehnge egudu njom jio ji Jehova, Esowo ebahre, ji yim go esamahr ebkpatahk Jehova.  
\v 30 Eji Finehas ji nlimanjom, a abafili ajahbe bo ji li atubesi abangenahb Isreel, wuku ana etˈtohngo ji Ruben, Gad, a ji Manase bungu no, yebe bo atahng sehng.  
\v 31 Owo Finehas mmon no Elieja ji nlimanjom kehm bungu tong anebe Ruben, Gad, a Manase re, <<Lela wahr ebkahn re Jehova li a nahre, tibre ń ka ten Jehova fere senng-e njahm go ejum jia. Wahn eblim re erakatahng ji Jehova kˈgbo tub anebe Isreel.  
\v 32 Owo Finehas mmon no Elieja ji nlimanjom, a abafili ajahbe, feere kehnge go Kenan, go eboa nkon nyi bo je no, a anebe Ruben, Gad go Giled song tooro tong anebe Isreel.  
\v 33 Bo bele eyebatahng sehng, fere tehk Esowo go nfaange nyi bo wuku no. Ntoobo nyi ebta kpeem jol bo go atahng re bo song rannge ajahbe nya Ruben a Gad lene no.  
\v 34 Fvfo anebe Ruben, a anebe Gad kehm kake egudu njom jia mbing: Bo jo lungu re, ntianse nyi a, go elka elka enahre re Jehova Esowo bi. 
\c 23  
\s1 Asohro Alum Nya Josua Gohro Bung Tong Atubesi Isreel 
\p  
\v 1 Eji ma kang afung gbalee, Jehova ma ka Isreel erekekv go esamahr anebekv ebo, Josua ntubesi ebo ebsahb kˈkul,  
\v 2 á kehm lungu anebe Isreel kpee ba kono edi ajehng, anebkul nfam, atubesi nsoja, abalamalam, a atubesi abailimi ntum, kehm bungu tong bo re: Anv, me n sahb kˈkul.  
\v 3 Wahnfono antahng ebnyehn ejum ajehng ajehng ji Jehova Esowo ebahne ma lim a nfam ajahbe nyaa. Jehova Esowo ebahne antahng antahng wo noko ka-n.  
\v 4 Buumen ana m ma bak adi alehkelkv ka atˈtohngo enyahne, adi ndi kpee, nya nfam ajahbe nya ma sa, nya m ma ga go ebta, bomo go aya ma Jodan tete song rehng go agburu aya ma nne lˈkˈma nyehn egbuk jehko go erede nfam.  
\v 5 Jehova, Esowo ebahne, yefono antahng bahke kame bo yehke egahne esamahr. Á bahke temme bo yehke go egahne elbohngo, ń fere ko adi ndi ebo, ana Jehova Esowo ebahne nyame no.  
\v 6 <<Yiimen tˈtahne, belen ekunukpu, wahn toono ajehng ajehng ji bo nyono go nwera ntahm nyi Mosis. Kana gbake feere ejang eboblum afi ejang ebobkal.  
\v 7 Gberen, wahn kˈrod elnahne semme a erik nfam ajahbe nya ma sa egahne ellong, kana toono asowo ebo, jol kana lung abing asowo ebo, afi tir bo. Kana jo loko bo, jol kana gong kak bo.  
\v 8 Wo Soren asi wahn tub Jehova Esowo ebahne ejahm ana ń kp-e toono wuku wuku, tete rehng anv.  
\v 9 Jehova ebkam agburu, a atahntahn nfam ajahbe go egahne elbohngo. Tete rehng lela, nnene limm no ma mal yiim-n go egahne esamahr.  
\v 10 Nne awohng go egahne ellong jo kame ane atahltahl nkpe ebal atahl awubu, tibre Jehova Esowo ebahne bi jo nok ka-n, ana á nyame tong-n.  
\v 11 Gberen, nong Jehova, Esowo ebahne jo kor-n.  
\v 12 Wo ń lˈfere sennge Esowo njahm, song semme a erik ane ji sa nfam ejahbe nyia, fere song ko abon ebo go elbal, afi song bal abon ebo, jo lim nsol semme a bo.  
\v 13 Kahnen re Jehova Esowo ebahne nehm kpe kam nfam ajahbe nyao yehke go egahne esamahr. Fvfo bo bahke jolo na ana arim a akpoko ka-n, a nrꞌrare nyi bahke jo ruum-n go njahm, a ajoongo nya bahke jo jamme go amahr, tete ń tan go nnooba ndi nyi Jehova Esowo ebahne ka-n no.  
\v 14 Anv, n yahke ba eltahme ebim ejok. Ń kpꞌkahne kpee a ntim a ntim enyahne kpee, a atohko enyahne re, enyam na abehng limm go anoobo anyam kpee nya Jehova Esowo ebahne nyame no tong-n, bi ma kꞌkane. Anyam kpee ebbiingi go nseenge. Jol na abehng kanem.  
\v 15 Wo ana anoobo anyam kpee nya Jehova Esowo ebahne, ma jol go nseenge ka-n, ano wo Jehova bahke koko abˈbi nsol kpee nya á tong-n no, ba kun-n, tete á ranng-n go nnooba ndi nyi á ka-n no.  
\v 16 Ń lꞌsoodo egbanngalung ji Jehova Esowo ebahne, nyi á ka-n elkahn, fere tahm song loko asowo nyandiki, fere gong kak bo, erakatahng ji Jehova bahke gboko kuum-n ana agun, fvfo ḿ bahke kpoko elwaare go nnooba ndi nyi á ka-n no. 
\c 24  
\s1 Anebe Isreel Kpe Tuungu Lim Egbanngalung Go Sekem 
\p  
\v 1 Owo Josua kehm kuku atˈtohngo nya Isreel kpee re bo lohng ba go Sekem. Á lungu anebkul, atubesi, abalamalam, a atubesi nsoja ba Isreel, bo ba yiimi go esamahr bi Esowo.  
\v 2 Josua kehm bungu tong bo re, <<Ji ji a ji Jehova Esowo bi Isreel kpˈbungu: Mahne mahne babnso ewahne, lene go egbuk aya Yufritis jehko jo kak asowo nyako, nne awohng go ebo ellong bo jo lung-e re Tera ji jolo nde no Ebraham abola Naho.  
\v 3 N yehke nso ewahne Ebraham go egbuk aya jio, tv-e ba rehng go Kenan. N ka-e abon gbalee. N ka-e Aesik,  
\v 4 n ka Aisik, Jekob abola Eso. Eso n ka-e edi awong awong ji li Siya. Jekob a abon ebe mehle song lene go Ijib. 
\p  
\v 5 << <Wo n kehm tumu Mosis abola Eron tv go Ijib. N kake anebe Ijib arem, go nsol nyi n limi o, n kehm-n yehke.  
\v 6 Eji n yehke babnso ewahne go Ijib, ń ba rehng go aya nkpafa anebe Ijib rodo amvtv akuungu, a abafingi anyˈnya ebo kam anebe Isreel tete rehng go aya nkpafa.  
\v 7 Bo rabe lung-m Jehova n kak bo ebo. Owo n kehm tumu ejannge tv go elka elka nꞌnahne a anebe Ijib. N tob limi aya nkpafa mele bo kpee. Ń tob nyehne go egahne amahr, nsol kpee nyi n limi anebe Ijib. Ń kange aya tvv go elka emahng ni kꞌlꞌmahng ajele. 
\p  
\v 8 << <N ko-n tete ba rehng go ndi nyi anebe Amor, bo ji lene ero bio bi aya Jodan. Bo noko a nahne, n faake bo kak-n go egahne abo, n rannge bo go egahne esamahr, fvfo ń song ko ndi abo.  
\v 9 Eji Balak ji mmona Jipo, ntula Moab, toobo ebjing bi á yahke ba elnoko a Isreel. Á kehm lungu Balam mmon no Beor re a ba biri nkuk tv-n.  
\v 10 Me, n wuungem Balam atung. Wo á soro na asi jo fuul-n, ano wo n tahr-n yehke go abo nya Balak. 
\p  
\v 11 Owo ń kehm siiri aya ma Jodan ba rehng go Jeriko. Anebe Jeriko kehm noko a na, a Amor, Peres, Kenan, Hiti, Gigas, Hivi, a Jebus, wo n yake bo kpee kak-n go abo.  
\v 12 N tumu agbunggbung, nya gbo-n mbang song kam bo go egahne esamahr, fvfo a atul abal ba anebe Amor. Ń limem jia go egahne ekahngkahng, a elban.  
\v 13 N ka-n ndi nyi ń ki lim eltum kehm bele, fere ka-n agburu ajahbe nya ń ki si, ń lene o, kpꞌlehke akab agreb a akab oliv, nya ń ki bahm. 
\p  
\v 14 Anv, fahlen Jehova, wahn fere lok-e, a ntim a ntim enyahne kpee. Roon asowo nya babnso ewahne jo kak go egbuk aya jehko, a Ijib, wahn fere jo kak Jehova.  
\v 15 Yehken lela nne no ḿ bahke kake. Lˈfere jol re wahn nehme yebe atahng re wahn kak Jehova. Ń kpˈsebe re wahn kak asowo nya babnso ewahne jo kak go egbuk aya Yufritis jehko , afi asowo nya anebe Amor kpo kak, bo ji ń lene go ebo a ndi? Wo, me a etahk etahk ejame e bahke kake Jehova. 
\p  
\v 16 Wo bo kehm faange re, <<Ndan gbaa re, wahr ten Jehova, fere kak asowo nyako!  
\v 17 Jehova Esowo abahre wo yehk-r antahng, a babnsoo ewahre go Ijib, ndi nyi e woomo eju. Á limi agburu akpokosi go egahre amahr, fere baab-r go eljen enahre kpee, go ellong nfam ajahbe nya e jo sehng ebo alatahkgur.  
\v 18 Jehova kame ajahbe kpee yehke go egahre esamahr, a anebe Amor ba lene go ndi nyia. Wahr fvfo, e bahke loko Jehova, tib ye wo li Esowo ebahre.>> 
\p  
\v 19 Josua kehm bungu tong ane re, <<Wahn nehm ma loko Jehova. Á li Esowo bi li saang, á kpo kpu elkahre. Á nehm tiki tahm ka-n go egahne etahnsi, a abiafem enyahne.  
\v 20 Ń lꞌten Jehova, fere jo kak asowo nyandiki, á bahke sennge fere ko elrannge ba ka-n, fere ranng-n, jol eji á ma-n tohko tib nnoobo enye. 
\p  
\v 21 Ane bao kpee kehm faange Josua re, <<Eꞌee, wahr ebyehke re e bahke loko Jehova.>> 
\p  
\v 22 Josua kehm bungu re, <<Wahnfono ba li atianse ka ji ḿ ma bung re, ḿ bahke loko Jehova.>> Bo kehm-e faange re, <<Wahr li atianse a ji e ma bung.>> 
\p  
\v 23 Josua kehm tongo bo re, <<Ebnob, anv ro-n asowo nya ajahbe nyako go egahne ellong, wahn fere sennge ntim enyahne feere goji Jehova, Esowo bi Isreel.>> 
\p  
\v 24 Bo kehm bungu tong Josua re, <<E bahke loko Jehova, ye wo li Esowo ebahre. Ye ntahngtahng wo e bahke jo kpun-e.>> 
\p  
\v 25 Efung bio Josua ko nwongo a ane. O Sekem wo, á ka bo ajehke a atahm  
\v 26 Josua yeele nsol nyia kpee go nwer atahm nyi Esowo. Á kehm bannge ekahmeltal song bum go nnahb eti oak nyi jolo kohlo ebkpatahk Jehova bi li saang. 
\p  
\v 27 Josua kehm bungu tong bo kpee re, <<Nyehn-n! Eltal nia bahke yiimi ntianse bada nahre. Eltal nia ebwuk alum kpee nya Jehova ma bung anahre eltal nia bahke yiimi ntianse bade anahne, ń tohko jol go etingitingi a Esowo ebahne. 
\p  
\v 28 Josua kehm yaame ane, nne awohng awohng feere kehnge go ege edi elehkelkv. 
\s1 Elkv ni Josua a Elieja 
\p  
\v 29 Eji nsol nyia kpee ma sehng, Josua mmon no Nun, nlokeltuma Jehova kehm ba kak elkv kpo. Á kange nnya atahl alon, a nnya ewubu kehm kpoko.  
\v 30 Bo kpa-e kak go Timnati Sera ji li edi awong awong ji Efriim , ejang ebobkal nfam bi egburu ewong Gaas. 
\p  
\v 31 Anebe Isreel kake Jehova nobnob ngare elkpin kpee ni Josua, a ngare elkpin kpee nyi anebkul ba kange sehnge Josua bo ji nyehne akpokosi nya Jehova ma lim ka anebe Isreel. 
\p  
\v 32 Akahb nya Josef, nya anebe Isreel rodo go Ijib ngare nyi bo mehle go Ijib, bo ba kpa kak go Sekem, go eji ndi ji Jekob gunu goji abone Hamo, ye ji jolo nde no Sekem. Bo gunu edi ndi jia go ebahk asilva atahl alon. Edi jia fere jolo edi elehkelkv ji ebangenahb, ji Josef. 
\p  
\v 33 Owo fvfo Elieja mmona Eron kehm ba kpo, bo kake go Gibia, edi jio ji bo ka Finehas mmon ewe, edi awong awong ji Efriim.